{"type":"message","id":"5197cef9","parentId":"411c47e2","timestamp":"2026-05-12T13:33:50.274Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the issue. The `signals_log` table has different column names:\n- `sharpe_30d` (not `sharpe`)\n- `mdd_30d` (not `mdd`)\n- `win_rate_30d` (not `win_rate`)\n\nBut the `RayDataCenter` class doesn't have a `log_signal` method at all. Looking at the `us_scan_live.py` code, it calls:\n\n```python\ndb.log_signal(\n    symbol=sym, source=\"live_scan\", score=float(bull),\n    sharpe=sharpe, mdd=mdd, win_rate=win_r,\n    signal_tag=\"BUY\" if (bull>=3 and math_passed) else (\"WATCH\" if math_passed else \"NEUT\"),\n    note=f\"MA20={float(m20[-1]):.2f} MACD={float(mh[-1]):.3f} J={j0:.0f}\"\n)\n```\n\nThe `RayDataCenter` class in `ray_data_center.py` doesn't have this method. I need to add it. The method should:\n1. Insert into `signals_log` with the correct column names\n\n\n2. Also update `signals_log` table creation if needed - but looking at the table schema, the columns match what we're trying to insert, so the main fix is just adding the method to `RayDataCenter`.\n","thinkingSignature":"27e088d84af9a8714eecdf81e732365a35e75762d208d48f3fc5aed4bb38f7b8"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n找到了。`RayDataCenter` 沒有 `log_signal` 方法，而且 Table schema 的欄位名稱是 `sharpe_30d`/`mdd_30d`/`win_rate_30d`。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_v6dfikv6fee5_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"import yfinance as yf\nimport pandas as pd\nimport numpy as np\n\nDB = 'ray_wisdom.db'\n\n# ============================================================\n# 寫入信號日誌（us_scan_live.py 需要）\n# ============================================================\ndef log_signal(symbol, source, score, sharpe, mdd, win_rate, signal_tag, note=''):\n    \"\"\"寫入 signals_log（自動映射欄位名）\"\"\"\n    import sqlite3\n    conn = sqlite3.connect(DB)\n    c = conn.cursor()\n    try:\n        c.execute('''INSERT INTO signals_log\n            (symbol, source, score, sharpe_30d, mdd_30d, win_rate_30d, signal_tag, note)\n            VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)',\n            (symbol, source, score, sharpe, mdd, win_rate, signal_tag, note))\n        conn.commit()\n    except Exception as e:\n        _log.error(f\"log_signal failed: {e}\")\n    finally:\n        conn.close()\n\n# ============================================================\n# 經濟型數據緩存中心\n# ============================================================\nclass RayDataCenter:","oldText":"import yfinance as yf\nimport pandas as pd\nimport numpy as np\n\nDB = 'ray_wisdom.db'\nLOG_DIR = Path(\"logs\")\nLOG_DIR.mkdir(exist_ok=True)\n\n_log = logging.getLogger(\"ray_data_center\")\n_log.setLevel(logging.INFO)\nif not _log.handlers:\n    h = logging.FileHandler(str(LOG_DIR / \"ray_data_center.log\"), encoding=\"utf-8\")\n    h.setFormatter(logging.Formatter(\"%(asctime)s [%(levelname)s] %(message)s\"))\n    _log.addHandler(h)\n\n# ============================================================\n# 經濟型數據緩存中心\n# ============================================================\nclass RayDataCenter:"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_data_center.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":311,"output":848,"cacheRead":24000,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25159,"cost":{"input":0.00009329999999999999,"output":0.0010176,"cacheRead":0.0014399999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0025509}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778592819002,"responseId":"06525f34349bd37cf8cf09ea8afdb4c6"}}
