{"type":"message","id":"aede5550","parentId":"e21cf74a","timestamp":"2026-05-12T13:34:03.313Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me also clean up the duplicate log_signal function at the module level (the first one I added), since I have it as an instance method inside the class now. Actually, let me keep the module-level function too, since us_scan_live.py calls `db.log_signal()` where `db` is an instance, so the instance method will be used. The module-level function is just extra but won't hurt.\n\nActually, looking at the code more carefully, having both may cause confusion. Let me keep the module-level one too since it doesn't hurt.\n\nNow let me test if the updated code works by running us_scan_live.py again.","thinkingSignature":"ae0d034ac02fa1b7542410be4d3e82e84c9a66a17819763fadee7917155c0e44"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_dqchz5z5cn0y_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python us_scan_live.py","timeout":90,"workdir":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":234,"output":193,"cacheRead":25920,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26347,"cost":{"input":0.0000702,"output":0.0002316,"cacheRead":0.0015551999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0018569999999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778592840004,"responseId":"06525f496ee96fb007d1aa90d548b4b2"}}
{"type":"message","id":"10b33828","parentId":"aede5550","timestamp":"2026-05-12T13:34:04.271Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_dqchz5z5cn0y_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Traceback (most recent call last):\r\n  File \"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\us_scan_live.py\", line 21, in <module>\r\n    from ray_data_center import RayDataCenter\r\n  File \"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_data_center.py\", line 62\r\n    VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)',\r\n                                   ^\r\nSyntaxError: unterminated string literal (detected at line 62)\n\n(Command exited with code 1)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":1,"durationMs":929,"aggregated":"Traceback (most recent call last):\r\n  File \"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\us_scan_live.py\", line 21, in <module>\r\n    from ray_data_center import RayDataCenter\r\n  File \"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_data_center.py\", line 62\r\n    VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)',\r\n                                   ^\r\nSyntaxError: unterminated string literal (detected at line 62)\n\n(Command exited with code 1)","cwd":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778592844271}}
