 getting squeezed: Liz Everett Krisberg. EBay rejects GameStop’s $56 billion takeover bid. Why joining the family business was James Reed’s hardest decision — and why it paid off.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"1499ff5dedc7ac3a\\\">>>\",\n      \"score\": 0.9991239\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3eb32a5cf8eef973\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nPremarket | Futures | Pre-market Trading - Markets Insider\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3eb32a5cf8eef973\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://markets.businessinsider.com/premarket\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b7da1ca00d2b9cbf\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n## US STOCK MARKETS FUTURES. | [FTSE 100](/index/ftse_100) | 10,228.00 | 39.00 | 0.38 % | 12:45:17 PM EDT 5/11/2026 |. | [IBEX 35](/index/ibex_35) | 17,852.50 | -36.90 | -0.21 % | 11:35:30 AM EDT 5/11/2026 |. | [OMXS30](/index/omx) | 3,079.45 | 5.77 | 0.19 % | 11:29:58 AM EDT 5/11/2026 |. | [USD/EUR](/currencies/usd-eur) | 0.8513 | 0.0027 | 0.31 % | 09:03:57 AM |. ## Commodity Futures. | [Gold Futures](/commodities/gold-price) |  |  | -0.74 % | 09:03:53 AM |. | [Silver Futures](/commodities/silver-price) |  |  | -1.71 % | 09:03:53 AM |. | [Oil (WTI) Futures](/commodities/oil-price?type=wti) |  |  | 3.11 % | 09:04:09 AM |. | [Oil (Brent) Futures](/commodities/oil-price?type=brent) |  |  | 2.48 % | 08:54:08 AM |. Here you can find premarket quotes for relevant stock market futures (e.g. Dow Jones Futures, Nasdaq Futures and S&P 500 Futures) and world markets indices, commodities and currencies. Real-time data shown for indices, futures, commodities or cryptocurrencies are provided by market makers, not the exchanges.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b7da1ca00d2b9cbf\\\">>>\",\n      \"score\": 0.9985562\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"8d9312324f613b68\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nMorning Report May 12, 2026 - Morning Report - World Indices\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"8d9312324f613b68\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.investtech.com/main/market.php?MarketID=992&product=38\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"9cd98739f17fb6ad\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n*   [Products](https://www.investtech.com/main/market.php?CountryID=992&p=staticPage&fn=products). *   [Research](https://www.investtech.com/main/market.php?CountryID=992&p=staticPage&fn=helpResearchMain). | [Login](javascript:void(0))[Free Trial](https://www.investtech.com/main/market.php?CountryID=992&product=0&lp=trial). ![Image 31](https://www.investtech.com/main/di.php?src=ndx_ndx/history/comment/2026/05/99200003_20260511.png)NASDAQ has broken up from an approximate horizontal trend channel in the medium long term. ![Image 32](https://www.investtech.com/main/di.php?src=ndx_ndx/history/comment/2026/05/99200056_20260511.png)Investors have paid higher prices over time to buy Nikkei 225 and the index is in a rising trend channel in the medium long term. ![Image 33](https://www.investtech.com/main/di.php?src=ndx_ndx/history/comment/2026/05/99200014_20260511.png)Toronto shows strong development within a rising trend channel in the medium long term. ![Image 34](https://www.investtech.com/main/di.php?src=ndx_ndx/history/comment/2026/05/99200070_20260511.png)S&P 200 is within an approximate horizontal trend channel in the medium long term, which indicates further development in the same direction. ![Image 35](https://www.investtech.com/main/di.php?src=ndx_ndx/history/comment/2026/05/99200052_20260511.png)Singapore - Straits Times has broken the floor of the rising trend channel in the medium long term, which indicates a weaker initial rising rate. ![Image 36](https://www.investtech.com/main/di.php?src=ndx_ndx/history/comment/2026/05/99200073_20260511.png)Nifty 50 is within an approximate horizontal trend channel in the medium long term, which indicates further develop