{"type":"message","id":"be701cf9","parentId":"a0cc35c4","timestamp":"2026-05-12T14:08:31.925Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"VICR - Vicr Corporation. Let me analyze this carefully:\n\n**Price: $293.07**\n\n**Technical:**\n- MA20 = $254.63, MA60 = $210.95\n- Price is ABOVE both MA20 and MA60 - bullish trend\n- Price is +$38.44 above MA20, +$82.12 above MA60 → strong uptrend\n\n**Indicators:**\n- RSI = 63.2 → healthy, not overbought (below 70)\n- MACD hist = 1.589 → positive, bullish\n\n\n- KDJ shows J值 at 77.3, down from 162.8 but still above the midline\n\n**Performance metrics:**\n- Sharpe ratio of 3.169 is exceptional\n- Maximum drawdown of 33.62% is concerning though\n- Win rate of 63.71% is solid\n- 5-day momentum at +10.17% and 20-day at +54.17% show strong recent performance\n\n**Signal assessment:**\n- We have 3 out of 4 bullish conditions met, but the signal is neutral because the maximum drawdown exceeds the 15% threshold at 33.62%\n- The stock is extended above its moving averages with RSI in healthy territory and MACD confirming momentum\n- Today's 6.36% drop on elevated volume suggests profit-taking after the recent rally\n- Despite excellent trend metrics (Sharpe 3.169, 63.71% win rate), the portfolio can't pass the math gate due to the large drawdown\n- VICR appears to be a high-volatility power electronics play with extreme recent strength (+54% over 20 days), but the risk profile disqualifies it for now","thinkingSignature":"2eedbb3c88dea7c2499beba347910e4c745955c1ed2838720d3f5bb5a1781af6"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n📊 **VICR 分析（2026-05-12）**\n\n**Vicor Corporation — 高功率電源模組供應商**\n\n---\n\n**💹 報價**\n| 價格 | MA20 | MA60 | 1日 | 5日 | 20日 |\n|------|------|------|-----|-----|------|\n| $293.07 | 254.63 | 210.95 | **-6.36%** | +10.17% | **+54.17%** |\n\n---\n\n**📐 技術指標**\n| 指標 | 數值 | 判讀 |\n|------|------|------|\n| RSI | 63.2 | ✅ 健康，沒有超買 |\n| MACD Hist | **+1.589** | 🟢 多方動能 |\n| KDJ J值 | **77.3 → 162.8** | 🟡 J值從超高區回落 |\n| MA20/MA60偏離 | +$38 / +$82 | 🟢 大幅高於均線 |\n\n---\n\n**📈 數學把關**\n| 項目 | 數值 | 門檻 | 結果 |\n|------|------|------|------|\n| Sharpe | **3.169** | > 1.5 | ✅ 極優秀 |\n| MDD | **33.62%** | < 15% | ❌ **超標（最大問題）** |\n| Win Rate | **63.71%** | > 45% | ✅ 優秀 |\n| 20日動能 | +54.17% | — | 🟢 極強 |\n\n---\n\n**🎯 結論：NEUT（旁觀）**\n\n**核心問題：MDD 33.62% >> 15% 紅線**\n- Sharpe 3.169 說明策略體質好，**但波動太大**\n- 今日 -6.36% 且成交量 338K（低於昨日 1.78M），**獲利了結跡象**\n- 20日線暴漲 +54%，等於從低點搶上來，已經很多人在賣\n\n**技術面支撐：**\n- MA20 = $254 是第一道防線\n- MA60 = $210 是更深層支撐\n- 價格仍在 MA20 之上，多方結構未破壞\n\n**Ray 判斷：**\n> VICR 不是爛股票，20日 +54% 動能驚人。但 **MDD 33% 是系統性風險**，你的 AGENTS.md 明確規定 MDD < 15% 才能交易。\n\n**等什麼：**\n- 等 MACD 柱狀圖明顯收斂 + KDJ J 值回落至 30 以下\n- 等待回測 MA20（$254）守住，再考慮佈局\n- 目前不適合重倉，風險報酬比不好"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":557,"output":980,"cacheRead":51360,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52897,"cost":{"input":0.0001671,"output":0.001176,"cacheRead":0.0030816,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0044247}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778594885398,"responseId":"06526747be1b5abfddec7ab57741e1db"}}
