{"type":"message","id":"503d845f","parentId":"e3c19719","timestamp":"2026-05-12T14:16:43.316Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_wn8uv1l8fyfq_1","toolName":"sessions_history","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"sessionKey\": \"agent:ray:telegram:direct:1616824689\",\n  \"messages\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"CNBC premarket page returned only CSS. Let me search for market news instead.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_function_t8otcqdluaum_1\",\n          \"name\": \"web_search\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"count\": 5,\n            \"query\": \"US stock market premarket outlook May 12 2026\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"minimax\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1778594614615,\n      \"responseId\": \"0652663935d642decbe534e5932cb25d\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"a2bdc398\",\n        \"seq\": 71\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"Now I have market context. Let me synthesize:\\n\\n1. CPI data shows consumer prices rose 3.8% annually in April - highest since May 2023 (inflation concerns)\\n2. WTI Oil up 3.11% (energy cost pressure)\\n3. NASDAQ broke up from horizontal trend channel (bullish medium-term)\\n4. Pre-market movers: APA +281%, MRNA +227%, MDB +199% (explosive movers)\\n5. Market under pressure from inflation data\\n\\nNow let me synthesize the technical scan + momentum data with market context for Jo.\\n\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"\\n\\n📊 **美股開盤分析 — 2026-05-12（台北 21:57，美股盤前）**\\n\\n---\\n\\n**🌐 市場宏觀背景**\\n\\n| 指標 | 數據 | 解讀 |\\n|------|------|--