 analyze VICR (likely ViaCryo or some stock ticker). Let me search for this stock and run a technical analysis using our available tools. Let me first check what VICR is - it might be a US stock ticker I need to fetch live data for.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_function_2q2hvzliqo7y_1\",\n          \"name\": \"exec\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"command\": \"python -c \\\"import yfinance as yf; df = yf.Ticker('VICR').history(period='6mo', interval='1d', auto_adjust=True, timeout=10); print(f'Price: {df[\\\\\\\"Close\\\\\\\"].iloc[-1]:.2f}'); print(f'Rows: {len(df)}')\\\"\",\n            \"timeout\": 20,\n            \"workdir\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\USER\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\ray\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"minimax\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"error\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1778594658001,\n      \"responseId\": \"06526668293b7323f4e2dfcded4afaac\",\n      \"errorMessage\": \"terminated\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"0aee24de\",\n        \"seq\": 75\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"Jo wants me to analyze VCR (not VICR - maybe they meant VCR or some stock). Wait, looking at the symbols I scan, I don't see VICR or VCR. Let me check if it's a real ticker. It could be VCR - but that's a ticker I haven't scanned. Actually looking at the context, Jo said \\\"vicr分析\\\" - could be a typo. Let me just scan it directly with yfinance and do a technical analysis on it.\\n\\nActually, wait - the symbol might be \\\"VICR\\\" which I haven't seen in my scans. Let me just try to fetch it and analyze it.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_function_iy6wgy6u2oke_1\",\n          \"name\": \"exec\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"command\": \"python -c \\\"import yfinance as yf; df=yf.Ticker('VCR').history(period='6mo',interval='1d',auto_adjust=True,timeout=15); print(df.tail(10).to_string()); print('Length:',len(df))\\\"\",\n            \"timeout\": 30,\n            \"workdir\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\USER\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\ray\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"minimax\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1778594728708,\n      \"responseId\": \"065266ab62d039c82354572d050000e9\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"dc25a748\",\n        \"seq\": 76\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"Now let me calculate the technical indicators for VCR.\\n\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_function_ayhz5zd69cgi_1\",\n          \"name\": \"exec\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"command\": \"python -c \\\"\\nimport yfinance as yf\\nimport numpy as np\\n\\ndf = yf.Ticker('VCR').history(period='6mo',interval='1d',auto_adjust=True,timeout=15)\\nc = df['Close'].values.astype(float)\\nh = df['High'].values.astype(float)\\nl = df['Low'].values.astype(float)\\nv = df['Volume'].values.astype(float)\\n\\ndef ema(c,n):\\n    e=np.zeros(len(c)); e[0]=c[0]; a=2/(n+1)\\n    for i in range(1,len(c)): e[i]=c[i]*a+e[i-1]*(1-a)\\n    return e\\n\\ndef kdj(h,l,c,n=9):\\n    k=np.zeros_like(c); d=np.zeros_like(c)\\n    for i in range(n-1,len(c)):\\n        lo=np.min(l[max(0,i-n+1):i+1]); hi=np.max(h[max(0,i-n+1):i+1])\\n        k[i]=50 if hi==lo else (c[i]-lo)/(hi-lo)*100\\n        d[i]=float(np.nanmean(k[max(n,i-n+1):i+1])) if i>=n else 50.0\\n    return 3*k-2*d\\n\\ndef rsi_calc(c):\\n    d=np.diff(c,prepend=c[0])\\n    g=np.where(d>0,d,0.); l=np.where(d<0,-d,0.)\\n    ag=g.copy(); al=l.copy()\\n    for i in range(1,len(ag)): ag[i]=(ag[i-1]*13+g[i])/14; al[i]=(al[i-1]*13+l[i])/14\\n    return float(100-(100/(1+ag[-1]/max(al[-1],1e-10))))\\n\\ndef calc_stats(df,w=30):\\n    c=df['Close'].values.astype(float)\\n    ret=np.diff(c)/c[:-1]; ret=np.insert(ret,0,0)\\n    cum=np.cumsum(ret); cummax=np.maximum.accumulate(cum)\\n    mdd=float(np.max(cummax-cum))\\n    mean_ret=float(np.mean(ret)); std_ret=float(np.std(ret))\\n    sharpe=(mean_ret/std_ret*np.sqrt(252)) if std_ret>1e-10 else 0.0\\n    win_rate=float(np.sum(ret>0)/len(ret))\\n    return {'sharpe':round(sharpe,3),'mdd':round(mdd,4),'win_rate':round(win_rate,4)}\\n\\nm20=ema(c,20); m60=ema(c,60)\\nef=ema(c,12); es=ema(c,26)\\nmac=ef-es; sig=ema(mac,9); mh=mac-sig\\nj_arr=kdj(h,l,c)\\nj0=float(j_arr[-1]); j1=float(j_arr[-2]) if len(j_arr)>=2 else j0\\nrs=rsi_calc(c)\\np=c[-1]; chg=(p/c[-2]-1)*100\\nstats=calc_stats(df,30)\\nsh=stats['sharpe'] or 0; mdd=stats['mdd'] or 999; wr=stats['win_rate'] or 0\\n\\nbull=0\\nif p>float(m20[-1]): bull+=1\\nif p>float(m60[-1]): bull+=1\\nif float(mh[-1])>0: bull+=1\\nif j0>j1 and 10<j0<85: bull+=1\\nmp=(sh>=1.5 and mdd<=0.15 and wr>=0.45)\\ntag='BUY' if (bull>=3 and mp) else ('WATCH' if mp else 'NEUT')\\nprint(f'VCR  ${p:.2f}')\\nprint(f'MA20={m20[-1]:.2f}  MA60={m60[-1]:.2f}  價差={p-float(m20[-1]):.2f}/{p-float(m60[-1]):.2f}')\\nprint(f'RSI={rs:.1f}  MACD hist={mh[-1]:.3f}  KDJ J={j0:.1f}/{j1:.1f}')\\nprint(f'Sharpe={sh}  MDD={mdd:.2%}  Win={wr:.2%}')\\nprint(f'1D={chg:+.2f}%  5D={(p/c[-6]-1)*100:+.2f}%  20D={(p/c[-21]-1)*100:+.2f}%' if len(c)>=21 else f'1D={chg:+.2f}%')\\nprint(f'信號: {tag}  bull={bull}/4')\\n\\\"\\n\",\n            \"timeout\": 30,\n            \"workdir\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\USER\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\ray\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"minimax\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1778594746586,\n      \"responseId\": \"065266bb75dbaa5