{"type":"message","id":"d4b1d742","parentId":"0da4c350","timestamp":"2026-05-12T14:19:00.420Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand! \"7層蛋糕\" refers to the AI industry chain \"seven-layer cake\" concept that NVIDIA CEO Jensen Huang defined at GTC 2026, covering the complete AI Factory ecosystem from Energy/Power all the way up to Agentic AI/Apps. \n\nJo wants me to do a stock analysis based on this seven-layer framework. Let me now scan the key stocks from each layer and provide a comprehensive analysis. The user has already given me the framework - they want me to analyze stocks across these 7 layers:\n\n1. Energy & Power: CEG, BE, VST\n2. Compute Silicon: NVDA, INTC, AMD\n3. Memory & Storage: MU, SNDK, WDC, STX\n4. Networking: AVGO, MRVL, ANET\n5. Systems & Cooling: VRT, SMCI\n6. Foundation Models: MSFT, META, GOOGL\n7. Agentic AI: PLTR, CRWD, NOW\n\nLet me run the technical scan on all these stocks.\n","thinkingSignature":"f033ccf87ce97bf1e85c87d7813fd60ad44eccdcdf2bd331943f59ef60a1b70d"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n了解！AI 七層蛋糕架構。現在對各層核心標的跑技術掃描：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_06g3bx9tkcmk_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"import yfinance as yf\nimport numpy as np\n\nlayers = [\n    (\"Layer1-能源\", [\"CEG\",\"BE\",\"VST\"]),\n    (\"Layer2-半導體\", [\"NVDA\",\"INTC\",\"AMD\"]),\n    (\"Layer3-記憶體\", [\"MU\",\"SNDK\",\"WDC\",\"STX\"]),\n    (\"Layer4-網路\", [\"AVGO\",\"MRVL\",\"ANET\"]),\n    (\"Layer5-系統散熱\", [\"VRT\",\"SMCI\"]),\n    (\"Layer6-模型平台\", [\"MSFT\",\"META\",\"GOOGL\"]),\n    (\"Layer7-代理應用\", [\"PLTR\",\"CRWD\",\"NOW\"]),\n]\n\ndef ema(c, n):\n    e = np.zeros(len(c)); e[0] = c[0]; a = 2/(n+1)\n    for i in range(1, len(c)): e[i] = c[i]*a + e[i-1]*(1-a)\n    return e\n\ndef kdj(h, l, c, n=9):\n    k = np.zeros_like(c); d = np.zeros_like(c)\n    for i in range(n-1, len(c)):\n        lo = np.min(l[max(0,i-n+1):i+1]); hi = np.max(h[max(0,i-n+1):i+1])\n        k[i] = 50 if hi==lo else (c[i]-lo)/(hi-lo)*100\n        d[i] = float(np.nanmean(k[max(n,i-n+1):i+1])) if i>=n else 50.0\n    return 3*k-2*d\n\ndef rsi_calc(c):\n    d = np.diff(c, prepend=c[0])\n    g = np.where(d>0, d, 0.); l = np.where(d<0, -d, 0.)\n    ag = g.copy(); al = l.copy()\n    for i in range(1, len(ag)): ag[i] = (ag[i-1]*13+g[i])/14; al[i] = (al[i-1]*13+l[i])/14\n    return float(100-(100/(1+ag[-1]/max(al[-1], 1e-10))))\n\ndef calc_stats(df, w=30):\n    c = df['Close'].values.astype(float)\n    ret = np.diff(c)/c[:-1]; ret = np.insert(ret, 0, 0)\n    cum = np.cumsum(ret); cummax = np.maximum.accumulate(cum)\n    mdd = float(np.max(cummax - cum))\n    mean_ret = float(np.mean(ret)); std_ret = float(np.std(ret))\n    sharpe = (mean_ret/std_ret*np.sqrt(252)) if std_ret>1e-10 else 0.0\n    win_rate = float(np.sum(ret>0)/len(ret))\n    return {'sharpe': round(sharpe,3), 'mdd': round(mdd,4), 'win_rate': round(win_rate,4)}\n\nprint(f\"AI 七層蛋糕技術掃描  2026-05-12\")\nprint(f\"{'Layer':<20}{'Ticker':<8}{'Price':>9}{'MA20':>9}{'MA60':>9}{'RSI':>7}{'MACD':>9}{'J':>8}{'1D%':>7}{'5D%':>7}{'20D%':>8} Sharpe  MDD\")\nprint(\"-\"*130)\n\nfor layer_name, syms in layers:\n    print(f\"\\n### {layer_name}\")\n    for sym in syms:\n        try:\n            df = yf.Ticker(sym).history(period=\"6mo\", interval=\"1d\", auto_adjust=True, timeout=10)\n            if df is None or len(df) < 60: continue\n            c = df['Close'].values.astype(float)\n            h = df['High'].values.astype(float)\n            l = df['Low'].values.astype(float)\n            m20 = ema(c,20); m60 = ema(c,60)\n            ef = ema(c,12); es = ema(c,26)\n            mac = ef-es; sig = ema(mac,9); mh = mac-sig\n            j_arr = kdj(h,l,c)\n            j0 = float(j_arr[-1]) if not np.isnan(j_arr[-1]) else 50.0\n            j1 = float(j_arr[-2]) if len(j_arr)>=2 else j0\n            rs = rsi_calc(c)\n            p = float(c[-1])\n            chg1 = (p/c[-2]-1)*100\n            chg5 = (p/c[-6]-1)*100 if len(c)>=6 else 0\n            chg20 = (p/c[-21]-1)*100 if len(c)>=21 else 0\n            stats = calc_stats(df, 30)\n            sh = stats['sharpe'] or 0; mdd_v = stats['mdd'] or 999\n            bull = 0\n            if p > float(m20[-1]): bull += 1\n            if p > float(m60[-1]): bull += 1\n            if float(mh[-1]) > 0: bull += 1\n            if j0>j1 and 10<j0<85: bull += 1\n            mp = (sh >= 1.5 and mdd_v <= 0.15 and stats['win_rate'] >= 0.45)\n            tag = \"🟢\" if (bull>=3 and mp) else \"🟡\" if (mp) else \"⚪\"\n            print(f\"{'':<20}{sym:<8}{p:>9.2f}{float(m20[-1]):>9.2f}{float(m60[-1]):>9.2f}\"\n                  f\"{rs:>7.1f}{float(mh[-1]):>9.3f}{j0:>8.1f}\"\n                  f\"{chg1:>6.1f}%{chg5:>6.1f}%{chg20:>7.1f}%\"\n                  f\"  {sh:.3f}  {mdd_v:.2%} {tag}\")\n        except Exception as e:\n            print(f\"{'':<20}{sym:<8} error: {e}\")\n        import time; time.sleep(0.2)\n","path":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\seven_layers_scan.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":8755,"output":1687,"cacheRead":59488,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69930,"cost":{"input":0.0026265,"output":0.0020244,"cacheRead":0.0035692799999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.008220179999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778595516910,"responseId":"065269c2e801c5e774717ec54c649bca"}}
