{"type":"message","id":"32f273a8","parentId":"fdce1d13","timestamp":"2026-05-12T14:27:45.964Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. I've set up the seven_layers_tracker.py script and executed it. Now let me create a cron job to run this tracking daily at US market open (21:30 Taiwan = 9:30 US ET), and then summarize the results for Jo.\n\nThe cron would be at 21:30 Taiwan time Mon-Fri which is 9:30 US ET. Let me create a cron job for this.\n\nAlso, I notice there are some price discrepancies between the scan earlier and now - the prices seem to have shifted. Let me present the results with the current scan and set up the cron job.","thinkingSignature":"23406b9fd0348a4684c3e1cf1d212bee568296f7b1e15c0a3e09b9da3583ce71"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n追蹤腳本已建立並即時掃描完成。幫你設定每日美股開盤後自動追蹤廣播：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qr3nlzaylhpr_1","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"add","job":{"name":"Ray 七層蛋糕每日追蹤","schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 22 * * 1-5","tz":"Asia/Taipei"},"payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"執行美股七層蛋糕追蹤：python seven_layers_tracker.py\n\n然後以【AI 七層蛋糕追蹤】為標題，格式化輸出所有20檔個股最新報價（Layer/代碼/價格/RSI/MACD/KDJ(J)/1D%/5D%/20D%/Sharpe/MDD），並給出輪動分析與操作建議。\n\n限時：90秒","timeoutSeconds":120},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"telegram","to":"1616824689"},"sessionTarget":"isolated"}}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":6327,"output":378,"cacheRead":101120,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":107825,"cost":{"input":0.0018981,"output":0.00045359999999999997,"cacheRead":0.006067199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0084189}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778596057935,"responseId":"06526bdbcccc798ad29aacc662c40092"}}
{"type":"message","id":"fbb0c3d4","parentId":"32f273a8","timestamp":"2026-05-12T14:27:46.587Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_qr3nlzaylhpr_1","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"id\": \"3b4a0b5a-35a4-4833-bdad-da5a9c0caeb6\",\n  \"agentId\": \"ray\",\n  \"sessionKey\": \"agent:ray:telegram:direct:1616824689\",\n  \"name\": \"Ray 七層蛋糕每日追蹤\",\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"createdAtMs\": 1778596066567,\n  \"updatedAtMs\": 1778596066567,\n  \"schedule\": {\n    \"kind\": \"cron\",\n    \"expr\": \"0 22 * * 1-5\",\n    \"tz\": \"Asia/Taipei\"\n  },\n  \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n  \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n  \"payload\": {\n    \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n    \"message\": \"執行美股七層蛋糕追蹤：python seven_layers_tracker.py\\n\\n然後以【AI 七層蛋糕追蹤】為標題，格式化輸出所有20檔個股最新報價（Layer/代碼/價格/RSI/MACD/KDJ(J)/1D%/5D%/20D%/Sharpe/MDD），並給出輪動分析與操作建議。\\n\\n限時：90秒\",\n    \"timeoutSeconds\": 120\n  },\n  \"delivery\": {\n    \"mode\": \"announce\",\n    \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n    \"to\": \"1616824689\"\n  },\n  \"state\": {\n    \"nextRunAtMs\": 1778680800000\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"id":"3b4a0b5a-35a4-4833-bdad-da5a9c0caeb6","agentId":"ray","sessionKey":"agent:ray:telegram:direct:1616824689","name":"Ray 七層蛋糕每日追蹤","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1778596066567,"updatedAtMs":1778596066567,"schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 22 * * 1-5","tz":"Asia/Taipei"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"執行美股七層蛋糕追蹤：python seven_layers_tracker.py\n\n然後以【AI 七層蛋糕追蹤】為標題，格式化輸出所有20檔個股最新報價（Layer/代碼/價格/RSI/MACD/KDJ(J)/1D%/5D%/20D%/Sharpe/MDD），並給出輪動分析與操作建議。\n\n限時：90秒","timeoutSeconds":120},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"telegram","to":"1616824689"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1778680800000}},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778596066586}}
{"type":"message","id":"527080e3","parentId":"fbb0c3d4","timestamp":"2026-05-12T14:27:56.606Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, the cron job is created. Now let me give Jo the summary with today's scan results.","thinkingSignature":"87e30eb30d9bb38bac09cf7acc65086fe782691d22045cb2cadffde0e402accf"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n✅ **已建立每日追蹤系統**\n\n**今晚數據（22:27）：**\n\n📊 **AI 七層蛋糕 — 2026-05-12 晚報**\n\n| 層 | 代碼 | 價格 | RSI | MACD | KDJ(J) | 1D% | 5D% | 20D% | Sharpe | MDD |\n|---|------|------|-----|------|--------|-----|-----|------|--------|-----|\n| L1 | CEG | $294 | 46 | -1.05 | -81 | -1.8% | -8.2% | -0.8% | -0.48 | 40% |\n| L1 | BE | $280 | 65 | -1.07 | 24 | -1.5% | -5.3% | +27.7% | 1.98 | 41% |\n| L1 | VST | $147 | 40 | -1.31 | -44 | -3.6% | -8.6% | -10.6% | -0.51 | 23% |\n| L2 | NVDA | $219 | 68 | +0.96 | 157 | +0.0% | +11.7% | +11.7% | 0.90 | 16% |\n| L2 | **AMD** | $449 | 78 | +10.40 | 76 | -2.1% | **+26.4%** | +76.1% | 1.99 | 28% |\n| L2 | **INTC** | $122 | 77 | +3.22 | 40 | -5.8% | +12.8% | **+91.1%** | 3.32 | 23% |\n| L3 | **MU** | $756 | 77 | +25.09 | 60 | -5.0% | +18.0% | +62.3% | 3.47 | 35% |\n| L3 | SNDK | $1435 | 69 | +33.39 | 29 | -7.3% | +2.0% | +51.9% | 3.55 | 33% |\n| L4 | ANET | $141 | 39 | -5.02 | -22 | +3.1% | -17.3% | -8.9% | 0.43 | 25% |\n| L5 | VRT | $358 | 65 | +2.07 | 54 | -2.7% | +4.9% | +15.2% | 2.56 | 22% |\n| L6 | GOOGL | $387 | 70 | +1.65 | -5 | -0.5% | -0.4% | +16.2% | 2.15 | 22% |\n| L7 | CRWD | $544 | 77 | +9.31 | 120 | +0.3% | +14.1% | +36.5% | 0.23 | 42% |\n\n---\n\n**🎯 輪動分析**\n\n**資金正在轉移：NVDA財報（5/28）前效應**\n\n| 方向 | 標的 | 訊號 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 🔴 L2→L1 轉移 | CEG/BE/VST 今日大跌，但 20D BE+27.7% 最強 | 能源補漲中 |\n| 🟡 L3 記憶體堅挺 | MU 20D +62%、SNDK +52% | HBM4 趨勢不變 |\n| 🟡 L7 資安突起 | CRWD 5D +14%、J=120 | AI資安剛啟動 |\n| ⚠️ L4 ANET 破線 | 5D -17.3%、RSI 39 | 網路股被拋售 |\n\n**Ray 今晚操作建議：**\n- **INTC（$122）** — 20D +91%，Sharpe 3.32，但 RSI 77 → 等回測 $115 再加\n- **AMD（$449）** — 5D +26%，AI備選晶片，RSI 78 偏高，輕倉\n- **MU（$756）** — 20D +62%，長期動能最強，但 MDD 35% 是系統風險\n- **VRT（$358）** — RSI 65 最健康，液冷龍頭，等 $350 以下再买\n\n**已設定每日 Cron（週一～五 22:00）自動追蹤並回報 📊**"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":595,"output":1048,"cacheRead":107424,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":109067,"cost":{"input":0.0001785,"output":0.0012576,"cacheRead":0.006445439999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00788154}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778596066589,"responseId":"06526be486b956ccd141de5ea4ea5d13"}}
