{"type":"message","id":"ab96744d","parentId":"96420bca","timestamp":"2026-05-12T14:40:52.675Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"`iq4_xs` doesn't seem to be a standard Ollama model. This is likely a custom model that Jo has locally or wants to use as a custom model name. Let me check what models are currently available and what Jo might be referring to.\n\nActually, `iq4_xs` might be a quantization format for a GGUF model like `qwen2.5-14b-instruct-q4_k_xs` or similar. It's a quantized variant of a larger model. \n\nLet me check if Jo has any local models that match this pattern.\n","thinkingSignature":"a7a43009e764dfdd5ae101db7e0e4a6c3a24471bac0ea7a1e00dcb3300cf1bc3"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_15t8ad8mbeyy_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ollama list","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":400,"output":152,"cacheRead":114208,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":114760,"cost":{"input":0.00011999999999999999,"output":0.0001824,"cacheRead":0.006852479999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.007154879999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778596847366,"responseId":"06526ef248ae6ce995b99de6eec32e28"}}
