{"type":"message","id":"e79860bc","parentId":"54417387","timestamp":"2026-05-12T14:43:55.560Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Jo is explaining that `iq4-xs` is a GGUF quantization format that needs to be downloaded from Hugging Face and imported via a Modelfile. This is specifically for Qwen 3.5 4B. Let me help Jo set this up.\n\nThe process:\n1. Download the IQ4_XS GGUF file from Hugging Face (e.g., from `mradermacher` or `bartowski`)\n2. Create a Modelfile\n3. Run `ollama create qwen35-4b-iq4xs -f Modelfile`\n4. Then `ollama run qwen35-4b-iq4xs`\n\n\nNow I need to locate the GGUF file on Hugging Face. I'm looking for either a Qwen 3.5 4B model with IQ4_XS quantization from a trusted creator like mradermacher, or the bartowski collection for Qwen 2.5 variants. Once I find the right file, I can help Jo set up the Modelfile and get everything running.","thinkingSignature":"1e509293e05a52af1d52b8c0e5d46f1beb3bc63f6c26d3079ffde2d58ee5a527"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_yxnwa68mvi53_1","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"maxChars":5000,"url":"https://huggingface.co/mradermacher/Qwen3.5-4B-Instruct-GGUF"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":114840,"output":279,"cacheRead":608,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":115727,"cost":{"input":0.034451999999999997,"output":0.0003348,"cacheRead":0.000036479999999999996,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03482328}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778596982708,"responseId":"06526fa21016a70d5f4ce5a300c23318"}}
