{"type":"message","id":"dc030c84","parentId":"19b572a8","timestamp":"2026-05-12T14:49:53.151Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me read the Modelfiles to see what base model they use.","thinkingSignature":"e5db589e56503e2f37f0ca0c1140e0a8a51e28df97cbe15b7883a9e70566dee4"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_400hgr9r72hu_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray-commander.Modelfile"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_400hgr9r72hu_2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray-v3.Modelfile"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":319,"output":95,"cacheRead":120544,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":120958,"cost":{"input":0.0000957,"output":0.00011399999999999999,"cacheRead":0.007232639999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0074423399999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778597388277,"responseId":"0652710eac951740b003b16029ae063a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"09ef4cac","parentId":"dc030c84","timestamp":"2026-05-12T14:49:53.162Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_400hgr9r72hu_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"FROM ray-deep-v1:latest\n\nSYSTEM \"\"\"\n你是 RAY-V3 QUANT COMMANDER，由 7B 參謀蒸餾後的 3B 實戰指揮官。\n\n[MASTER LOGIC ALIGNMENT]\n服從以下三大師邏輯：\n\n1. 塔雷伯 (Taleb) 肥尾防禦：\n   - 拒絕 Sharpe < 1.2 的平庸提案\n   - ATR 波幅超過 20 日均值 2 倍 → 啟動動態跟蹤止損\n\n2. 索普 (Thorp) 凱利執行：\n   - position_size 必須配合信心加權\n   - 信心 < 0.7 → 部位不超過總資產 5%\n\n3. 康諾斯 (Connors) 均值修正：\n   - RSI(2) < 10 超跌機會 + 配合外資籌碼流入校準\n\n[CONSTRAINTS]\n- 輸出純 JSON，無任何額外文字、解釋、廢話\n- 所有價格基於 yfinance 最後收盤價\n- 遵守以下 Schema\n\n[OUTPUT SCHEMA]\n{\n  \"strategy_name\": \"string\",\n  \"master_alignment\": \"Taleb/Thorp/Connors\",\n  \"action\": \"BUY/SELL/HOLD\",\n  \"confidence\": 0.00,\n  \"logic_bridge\": \"一句話說明大師邏輯\",\n  \"position_size_pct\": 0,\n  \"orders\": {\n    \"entry\": 0.0,\n    \"stop_loss\": 0.0,\n    \"take_profit\": 0.0\n  }\n}\n\"\"\"\n\nPARAMETER temperature 0.3\nPARAMETER num_ctx 4096\nPARAMETER num_predict 512\nPARAMETER top_p 0.85\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778597393162}}
{"type":"message","id":"e2b7a95b","parentId":"09ef4cac","timestamp":"2026-05-12T14:49:53.162Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_400hgr9r72hu_2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"FROM ray-v3:latest\n\n# qwen3.5:4b 的 Thinking Mode 是常駐行為\n# 不適合需要嚴格 JSON 輸出的交易指令場景\n# 保留給未來非結構化輸出任務\n# 任務時段調度：\n#   交易時段 → ray-v1（快速）\n#   盤後分析 → ray-deep-v1（深度，qwen2.5:7b，無 thinking mode）\n\nTEMPLATE \"\"\"\n{{- if .System }}<|im_start|>system\n{{ .System }}<|im_end|>\n{{ end }}<|im_start|>user\n{{ .Prompt }}<|im_end|>\n<|im_start|>assistant\n\"\"\"\n\nSYSTEM \"\"\"你是 Ray 量化交易 Agent。\n\n[MASTER ALIGNMENT]\n1. Taleb 肥尾： Sharpe<1.2 拒絕\n2. Thorp 凱利： 信心<0.7 部位≤5%\n3. Connors 均值： RSI(2)<10 超跌\n\n[OUTPUT]\n純 JSON，無其他：\n{\"strategy_name\":\"...\",\"action\":\"BUY/SELL/HOLD\",\"confidence\":0.0,\"logic_bridge\":\"...\",\"position_size_pct\":0,\"orders\":{\"entry\":0.0,\"stop_loss\":0.0,\"take_profit\":0.0}}\n\"\"\"\n\nPARAMETER temperature 0.3\nPARAMETER num_ctx 4096\nPARAMETER num_predict 512\nPARAMETER top_p 0.85\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778597393162}}
{"type":"message","id":"c594329d","parentId":"e2b7a95b","timestamp":"2026-05-12T14:50:02.205Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see:\n\n1. **ray-commander** = FROM ray-deep-v1 (i.e., qwen2.5:7b base) + Taleb/Thorp/Connors system prompt\n2. **ray-v3** = FROM qwen3.5:4b base + system prompt\n\nBut wait - ray-v3.Modelfile says \"FROM ray-v3:latest\" which means it's based on the `qwen3.5:4b` model. But looking at the Ollama list earlier: `ray-v3:latest 934626f142ac 3.4 GB`. \n\nThe 3.4 GB size matches qwen3.5:4b, so ray-v3 is indeed based on qwen3.5:4b.\n","thinkingSignature":"3c33b26639113fa0d59602fbc009732773a38502c537482e262382927ddea65e"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**ray-commander** 和 **ray-v3** 的底層模型：\n\n| 名字 | 基礎模型 | 備註 |\n|------|---------|------|\n| **ray-v3** | `qwen3.5:4b`（Qwen 3.5 四參數） | FROM qwen3.5:4b base |\n| **ray-commander** | `ray-deep-v1`（qwen2.5:7b） | FROM ray-deep-v1，疊加大師對齊 System Prompt |\n\n---\n\n**所以實際上：**\n- `ray-v3` — 基於 **Qwen 3.5-4B**（3.4GB），帶 Thinking Mode\n- `ray-commander` — 基於 **qwen2.5:7b**（4.7GB），由 ray-deep-v1 加上 Taleb/Thorp/Connors 三重大師邏輯蒸餾\n\n`ray-commander` = ray-deep-v1（qwen2.5:7B）+ 定制 System Prompt（交易員大師對齊），兩者都是 Jo 定制過的 Modelfile，不是 Ollama 官方版本。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":832,"output":415,"cacheRead":120832,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":122079,"cost":{"input":0.0002496,"output":0.000498,"cacheRead":0.007249919999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00799752}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778597393165,"responseId":"065271147f6265f89015e43bee2e5b16"}}
