{"type":"message","id":"2761ee49","parentId":"04ee50a1","timestamp":"2026-05-12T14:56:28.583Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Jo is showing me error logs from some system - it looks like a Python Streamlit app (using `use_container_width` which is a Streamlit parameter) and some Telegram errors about \"Unauthorized\" (HTTP 401).\n\nThe key issues I can see:\n1. `use_container_width` deprecation warnings from Streamlit - these need to be fixed in Streamlit code\n2. Telegram 401 Unauthorized error - the bot token might be invalid or the Telegram API key has issues\n\nHowever, looking at the context - Jo sent these error logs. The errors are from a different system (not directly Ray's workspace on this machine). The `use_container_width` is a Streamlit parameter, and the 401 error is a Telegram bot API issue.\n\n\nI should tackle the straightforward issues first: the Streamlit deprecation warning about `use_container_width` is easy to fix, and the Telegram 401 error suggests either an expired bot token or permission problems with the bot. Since this appears to be running on a server rather than Jo's local Windows machine, I'll focus on the most actionable items.","thinkingSignature":"8940d3c4135ff60c13b972a895cb5e1b95ce6828577ed76f5a8473b76527590c"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nJo 傳來的是別的系統的日誌（Streamlit + Telegram bot）。我這邊 Ray agent 的工作環境是獨立的，看不到你本機以外的服務。\n\n**兩個錯誤：**\n\n**1. Streamlit `use_container_width` 警告（deprecation）**\n- 這是 Streamlit 的參數，2025 年底後要停用\n- 需找到使用 `use_container_width=True` 的 `.py` 檔，替換成 `width='stretch'`\n- 這是其他 Agent（Tina）的程式碼，不是 Ray 的\n\n**2. Telegram HTTP 401 Unauthorized**\n- Bot token 失效或权限问题\n- 跟 Ray 這個 Telegram session 是不同 bot\n\n---\n\n**你是要我幫你：**\n1. 找出並修復 Tina 系統裡的 `use_container_width` 警告？（需知道 Tina 程式路徑）\n2. 還是 Telegram 401 的問題？（檢查 bot token）\n\n這兩個都不在我目前的 Ray 工作區內，需要你告訴我 Tina 的程式在哪裡或把相關檔案發過來。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":122519,"output":452