{"type":"message","id":"659d120c","parentId":"2535f4c2","timestamp":"2026-05-12T15:00:53.076Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is telling me this error is from Tina's Streamlit app running on Streamlit Cloud (`/home/adminuser/venv/`). The error shows it's still getting `use_container_width` warnings from their deployed Streamlit Cloud instance, and also shows a Telegram HTTP 401 error.\n\nThe `use_container_width` fix I made was to the local file at `C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\\streamlit_tw_stock.py`, but Streamlit Cloud runs the deployed version from their GitHub repo, not the local file. So the local fix doesn't automatically deploy.\n\nAlso the HTTP 401 Telegram error is from the Streamlit Cloud app's Telegram bot - it needs to send messages to Jo's Telegram but the bot token isn't authorized.\n\n\nThe real issue is that my fix is local, but the deployed app on Streamlit Cloud still has those warnings, so they'd need to push the updated code to their GitHub repo for it to take effect. The 401 error suggests the Telegram bot token being used there isn't properly configured or authorized for that bot.","thinkingSignature":"2ec79180f452b6de04cc11fc408dbea1f1cee05073b1766003723dfe602a790b"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n這個錯誤訊息是來自 **Streamlit Cloud 部署的 Tina 系統**，不是本地檔案。我剛才修復的是你本機的 `streamlit_tw_stock.py`，但 Streamlit Cloud 上跑的程式需要 **從 GitHub 重新部署** 才會生效。\n\n---\n\n**兩件事需要分開處理：**\n\n**1. use_container_width 警告**（本地已修復，但需重新部署）\n- 需把更新後的 `streamlit_tw_stock.py` commit 並 push 到 GitHub\n- Streamlit Cloud 需重新部署才生效\n- 我的本地修復在：`C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\\streamlit_tw_stock.py`\n\n**2. HTTP 401 Telegram 錯誤**（Streamlit Cloud Bot 問題）\n- Streamlit Cloud 上的 Telegram bot token 可能失效\n- 需要在 Streamlit Cloud secrets 重新設定 bot token\n\n---\n\n**你需要做：**\n1. 確認 GitHub 上的 `streamlit_tw_stock.py` 已更新（我剛才的修復）\n2. 到 Streamlit Cloud 重新 Deploy（或觸發 redeploy）\n3. 檢查 Streamlit Cloud 的 Secrets 有沒有設定正確的 Telegram bot token\n\n你是從哪個 GitHub repo 部署 Tina 的？我可以幫你檢查有沒有 other instances of `use_container_width`。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":5516,"output":507,"cacheRead":123488,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":129511,"cost":{"input":0.0016547999999999999,"output":0.0006083999999999999,"cacheRead":0.007409279999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.009672479999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778598040917,"responseId":"0652739c963d7676bc6c1f3e0aef7265"}}
