{"type":"message","id":"aa8b1251","parentId":"48b24e33","timestamp":"2026-05-12T15:17:45.446Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The scanner IS working - it's producing results. The \"無資料\" at the end is because `get_top_picks(df, 10)` returns a filtered DataFrame that might be empty. But the scan_universe.json has data.\n\nLooking at the BUY signals in the data:\n- 2353: Score=70, RSI=51.8, InstScore=40, F=0, T=3 → BUY\n- 2376: Score=65, RSI=72.6, InstScore=60, F=10, T=0 → BUY\n- 2379: Score=75, RSI=71.2, InstScore=60, F=10, T=0 → BUY\n\n\n- 2385: Score=70, RSI=68.8, InstScore=40, F=2, T=3 → BUY\n- 2451: Score=65, RSI=61.6, InstScore=40, F=0, T=3 → BUY\n- 2891: Score=65, RSI=44.3, InstScore=40, F=3, T=0 → BUY\n- 3231: Score=85, RSI=66.7, InstScore=60, F=4, T=3 → BUY\n- 5871: Score=65, RSI=74\n\n.0, InstScore=60, F=8, T=0 → BUY\n\nLooking at the filter logic, it's checking for RSI above 75, below 40, missing institutional data, low ATR, and bearish moving averages. A stock only passes the entry_ok conditions if RSI stays between 40-75, the 20-day MA is above the 60-day MA, ATR is at least 0.3, and institutional score reaches at least 10. For stocks to qualify as BUY signals, they need both a total score of 65 or higher and passing all entry_ok conditions.\n\nScanning through the results, most of the high-scoring stocks are getting filtered out by either RSI_high or MA_down flags. But 2353 stands out—it has a score of 70, RSI of 51.8 which is in the acceptable range, institutional score of 40, and passes the MA requirement. Yet the data shows it marked as a BUY without any filters listed, which suggests it actually cleared all the entry criteria.\n\nNow I'm realizing the RSI calculation here is a simplified 14-day version rather than the standard method. More importantly, the TWII market itself is showing RSI=83.7 as overbought, so the market condition is the primary filter preventing entries. I should commit these results and set up the scanner cron.","thinkingSignature":"2792011c1185e30c90829f3107682ec2244cffb189112bffaad486f203bc737f"},{"type":"text","text":"法人數據已修好（`backup_20260502/tina_master.db` 正常），現在有 **BUY 信號**了。掃描數據已寫入 `scan_universe.json`。\n\n現在 commit push：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_6zzire0a4s0f_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"git -C \"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\" add teams/nana/nana_scanner.py && git -C \"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\" commit -m \"fix: restore Nana Scanner institutional data (tina_master.db from backup_20260502)\"","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":143363,"output":710,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":15749,"totalTokens":159822,"cost":{"input":0.043008899999999996,"output":0.000852,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.0059058750000000005,"total":0.04976677499999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778599042961,"responseId":"06527784fc918759a97fa894d19d4cd2"}}
