{"type":"compaction","id":"0328c27d","parentId":"6d20fdcd","timestamp":"2026-05-12T15:32:02.964Z","summary":"\n\n## Goal\n1. Resume Nana Scanner (停滯12天) \n2. Delete Tina V3 Alpha (本體模組已不見)\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Nana Scanner 恢復運行\n- Tina V3 Alpha 完全刪除\n- Qwen3.5-4B-IQ4_XS.gguf 下載繼續（2.48GB，約50%完成）\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] **ray_data_center.py** — 新增 `log_signal()` 實例方法，修復 DB 寫入錯誤（SQL 三引號問題改為單行字串）\n- [x] **us_scan_live.py / us_momentum.py** — 美股技術掃描正常運行，QQQ 唯一 BUY 訊號\n- [x] **VICR 分析** — $293.07，Sharpe 3.169，MDD 33.62%（超標），訊號 NEUT\n- [x] **VCR 分析** — $390，MACD=-0.697，KDJ 死亡交叉，訊號 NEUT\n- [x] **AI 七層蛋糕掃描** — 建立 `seven_layers_tracker.py`，20檔股票每日追蹤，設定週一～五 22:00 cron\n- [x] **llm_router.py** — 所有本地分析統一改為 `ray-deep-v1`（7B），fast/deep/v3/alt_fast 全部指向 ray-deep-v1\n- [x] **ray_brain.py, ray_cloud_brain.py, ray_integrated_brain.py, ray_self_correct.py, tina_bridge.py, tina_daily_self_correct.py** — fast_model 改為 ray-deep-v1\n- [x] **check_vs_jo_design.py, step4_ollama_fallback.py, ray_integrity_booster.py** — 模型改為 ray-deep-v1\n- [x] **Ollama 刪除** — `ollama rm ray-v1` + `ollama rm qwen2.5:3b` + `ollama rm ray-v3`\n- [x] **streamlit_tw_stock.py** — `use_container_width=True` → `width='stretch'`（14處），backup 存至 `.bak`，已 commit + push 到 `jasontpc/Tina_Quant_System`\n- [x] **secrets.toml** — `tg_bot_token` 更新為 `8614615741:AAHWGhPeP3gMXs2EPGbDC3FWBaWHnT9jt1M`\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] **Qwen3.5-4B-IQ4_XS.gguf 下載** — 2.48GB 檔案，正在背景下載（約50%，session tender-orbit 已結束需重新確認進度）\n- [ ] **恢復 Nana Scanner** — 待執行\n- [ ] **刪除 Tina V3 Alpha** — 待執行\n\n### Blocked\n- Qwen3.5 下載：背景 session 已结束，需重新確認下載狀態並繼續\n- Nana Scanner 恢復：需確認路徑與版本（目前有 nana_v68 ~ v65，多個版本需確認用哪個）\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **全本地分析統一 ray-deep-v1**：Jo 決定所有本地 LLM 統一走 7B（ray-deep-v1），放棄 1.5B（ray-v1）\n- **AI 七層蛋糕框架**：L1能源(CEG/BE/VST)、L2半導體(NVDA/INTC/AMD)、L3記憶體(MU/SNDK/WDC/STX)、L4網路(AVGO/MRVL/ANET)、L5散熱(VRT/SMCI)、L6模型(MSFT/META/GOOGL)、L7代理(PLTR/CRWD/NOW)\n- **Streamlit deprecation 修復**：使用 `width='stretch'` 而非 `use_container_width=True`\n- **Tina V3 Alpha 刪除**：本體模組 `tina_v3_alpha_live.py` 缺失，只剩 cron 殼\n\n## Next Steps\n1. 檢查 Qwen3.5-4B-IQ4_XS.gguf 下載進度，確認是否完成\n2. 若下載完成：建立 Modelfile → `ollama create qwen35-4b-iq4xs` → 整合進 llm_router.py\n3. 刪除 Tina V3 Alpha：`Remove-Item C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\\teams\\tina_v3_alpha -Recurse -Force`\n4. 恢復 Nana Scanner：確認 nana_v68 是最新版本，重新執行並設定 cron\n5. Streamlit Cloud 的 Telegram 401 問題：Jo 需到 Streamlit Cloud dashboard 更新 `tg_bot_token` 為 `8614615741:AAHWGhPeP3gMXs2EPGbDC3FWBaWHnT9jt1M`\n\n## Critical Context\n- **Ollama 模型現況**：`ray-commander`（qwen2.5:7b）、`ray-deep-v1`（qwen2.5:7b）\n- **下載位置**：`C:\\Users\\USER\\AppData\\Local\\Programs\\Ollama\\models\\qwen35-4b-iq4xs\\Qwen3.5-4B-IQ4_XS.gguf`\n- **Git repo**：`https://github.com/jasontpc/Tina_Quant_System.git`\n- **Streamlit app**：`https://tinaquantsystem-rmpu5sfrce9a6s9ebw3moj.streamlit.app/`\n- **本地 secrets**：`C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\\.streamlit\\secrets.toml`\n- **Nana reports**：`C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\\teams\\nana\\reports\\`（最後掃描 2026-04-30）\n- **Tina V3 Alpha cron 腳本**：`C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\\teams\\tina_v3_alpha\\_cron_live_scan.py`（本體已失）\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n\n\n## Original Request\nJo wants two things:\n1. **Restore Nana Scanner** - make it functional again\n2. **Delete Tina V3 Alpha** - remove the incomplete/broken team folder\n\n## Early Progress\n- Assistant examined `teams/tina_v3_alpha/` and found only one file: `_cron_live_scan.py` (which imports a non-existent module `tina_v3_alpha_live`)\n- Checked Nana's git history and current state — `nana_scanner.py` exists in `teams/nana/`\n- **Critical issue found**: The scanner requires `skills/stock-analyzer/scripts/tina_master.db`, but the DB was found only in `backup_20260502/` — the live scripts directory doesn't exist\n- Assistant listed cron jobs and was examining them to find/fix Nana's scheduler\n\n## Context for Suffix\nThe conversation continues with examining cron jobs (which was truncated), looking for where Nana Scanner is scheduled and what needs to be fixed to make it operational.\n\n<read-files>\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\quick_test.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray-commander.Modelfile\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray-v3.Modelfile\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\us_scan_live.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\\teams\\nana\\nana_market_scanner.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\\teams\\nana\\nana_scanner.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\\teams\\nana\\reports\\nana_v68_scan_20260430.json\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\\teams\\tina_v3_alpha\\_cron_live_scan.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\Downloads\\Telegram Desktop\\ChatExport_2026-05-12\\messages.html\n</read-files>\n\n<modified-files>\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\check_tables.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\check_vs_jo_design.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\download_qwen35_iq4xs.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\find_model_refs.ps1\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\find_model_refs.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\find_streamlit.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\fix_streamlit_use_container.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\llm_router.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_brain.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_cloud_brain.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_data_center.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_integrated_brain.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_integrity_booster.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_self_correct.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\search_qwen.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\seven_layers_scan.py\nC:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\