{"type":"message","id":"c28fd385","parentId":"97faa26a","timestamp":"2026-05-12T15:49:38.527Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_98ro3cg2cboj_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\r\n# ── Page Setup ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\r\n\r\nst.set_page_config(page_title=\"Tina Scanner v3.1\", page_icon=\"📈\", layout=\"wide\")\r\n\r\nst.markdown(\"\"\"\"\r\n<style>\r\n.metric-card { background-color:white; padding:20px; border-radius:12px; box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); border-left:5px solid #1E88E5; }\r\n[data-testid=\"stMainBlockContainer\"] { padding-top:1rem; }\r\n</style>\r\n\"\"\", unsafe_allow_html=True)\r\n\r\nst.title(\"[UP] Tina Scanner v3.0 — TW+US Tech Scoring\")\r\n_log.info(\"[UI] Page setup complete\")\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\ntw_tab, us_tab = st.tabs([\"📊 Taiwan\", \"🇺🇸 US\"])\r\n\r\n# ── Market Overview ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────\r\n\r\ntry:\r\n\r\n    twii = yf.Ticker(\"^TWII\")\r\n\r\n    twii_hist = twii.history(period=\"1mo\")\r\n\r\n    spy = yf.Ticker(\"^GSPC\")\r\n\r\n    spy_hist = spy.history(period=\"1mo\")\r\n\n[1376 more lines in file. Use offset=1438 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778600978527}}
{"type":"message","id":"9b5b2fdd","parentId":"c28fd385","timestamp":"2026-05-12T15:49:47.050Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. I can see the current UI structure. Let me plan the B option carefully:\n\n**Current UI structure (line ~1411+):**\n1. `st.set_page_config` + CSS (already done)\n2. `st.title`\n3. `st.tabs` with Taiwan/US tabs\n4. Inside each tab: market overview metrics, then category selection, then scan button, then results table\n\n**Jo's v3.1 new UI elements to integrate:**\n1. Sidebar with filters (market choice, grade filter, min_score) - instead of having these in each tab\n2. `st.tabs` for scan vs deep analysis - currently we have Taiwan/US tabs\n\n\n3. Metric cards at the top for overview\n4. Individual stock deep analysis with metric-card HTML styling\n\nFor option B, I'll preserve the existing tab structure while moving the filters to a sidebar, enhance the market overview metrics to display as cards, and add a deep analysis section using the metric-card styling. The key is keeping all the current functionality while upgrading the visual presentation.\n\nThe biggest win here is moving grade_filter, min_score, and market_choice to the sidebar so they become global controls instead of being duplicated within each tab. I'll add a sidebar section, improve how the metric cards display, integrate the individual stock deep analysis card styling, and include toast notifications for scan completion.","thinkingSignature":"10a34af6e235bbcef64bed28bad79e5a6019b72d9ee5c5deeffa5d31ef8631d4"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_bwzr9cgoz7k9_1","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":70,"offset":1438,"path":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\\streamlit_tw_stock.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":375,"output":346,"cacheRead":95040,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":95761,"cost":{"input":0.0001125,"output":0.00041519999999999995,"cacheRead":0.0057024,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0062301}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778600978531,"responseId":"06527f14103ffc54c9e313adc30faf2a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"4ed8db09","parentId":"9b5b2fdd","timestamp":"2026-05-12T15:49:47.059Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_bwzr9cgoz7k9_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\r\n    if not twii_hist.empty and not spy_hist.empty:\r\n\r\n        # TW market\r\n\r\n        twii_close = twii_hist['Close'].iloc[-1]\r\n\r\n        twii_prev = twii_hist['Close'].iloc[-2]\r\n\r\n        twii_chg = (twii_close - twii_prev) / twii_prev * 100\r\n\r\n        twii_rsi = None\r\n\r\n        if len(twii_hist) >= 15:\r\n\r\n            d = twii_hist['Close'].diff()\r\n\r\n            g = d.clip(lower=0).rolling(14).mean()\r\n\r\n            l = (-d.clip(upper=0)).rolling(14).mean()\r\n\r\n            rs = g / l.replace(0, np.nan)\r\n\r\n            twii_rsi = float((100 - (100 / (1 + rs))).iloc[-1])\r\n\r\n        # US market (S&P 500)\r\n\r\n        spy_close = spy_hist['Close'].iloc[-1]\r\n\r\n        spy_prev = spy_hist['Close'].iloc[-2]\r\n\r\n        spy_chg = (spy_close - spy_prev) / spy_prev * 100\r\n\r\n        spy_rsi = None\r\n\r\n        if len(spy_hist) >= 15:\r\n\r\n            d2 = spy_hist['Close'].diff()\r\n\r\n            g2 = d2.clip(lower=0).rolling(14).mean()\r\n\r\n            l2 = (-d2.clip(upper=0)).rolling(14).mean()\r\n\r\n            rs2 = g2 / l2.replace(0, np.nan)\r\n\r\n            spy_rsi = float((100 - (100 / (1 + rs2))).iloc[-1])\r\n\r\n        rsi_label_tw = \"[ERR] 過熱\" if twii_rsi and twii_rsi > 70 else (\"[Y] 偏多\" if twii_rsi and twii_rsi > 50 else \"[G] 中性\")\r\n\r\n        rsi_label_us = \"[ERR] 過熱\" if spy_rsi and spy_rsi > 70 else (\"[Y] 偏多\" if spy_rsi and spy_rsi > 50 else \"[G] 中性\")\r\n\r\n        m = st.columns(6)\r\n\r\n        m[0].metric(\"TWII\", f\"{twii_close:,.0f}\", f\"{twii_chg:+.2f}%\")\r\n\r\n        m[1].metric(\"TWII RSI\", f\"{twii_rsi:.0f}\" if twii_rsi else \"N/A\")\r\n\r\n        m[2].metric(\"TW狀態\", rsi_label_tw)\r\n\r\n        m[3].metric(\"S&P500\", f\"{spy_close:,.0f}\", f\"{spy_chg:+.2f}%\")\r\n\r\n        m[4].metric(\"SPY RSI\", f\"{spy_rsi:.0f}\" if spy_rsi else \"N/A\")\r\n\r\n        m[5].metric(\"US狀態\", rsi_label_us)\r\n\r\nexcept Exception:\r\n\r\n    pass\r\n\r\n\r\n\n[1306 more lines in file. Use offset=1508 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778600987059}}
