{"type":"message","id":"abf388d9","parentId":"c643db09","timestamp":"2026-05-12T15:50:55.143Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_80vwj4odvyi4_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\r\n\r\n    # --- Single Stock Deep Analysis ---\r\n\r\n    st.divider()\r\n\r\n    st.subheader(\"Single Stock Deep Analysis\")\r\n\r\n    col_code, col_btn = st.columns([2, 1])\r\n\r\n    with col_code:\r\n\r\n        single_code = st.text_input(\"Stock Code\", \"2330\", key=\"tw_single_code\").strip().upper()\r\n\r\n    with col_btn:\r\n\r\n        st.write(\" \")\r\n\r\n        do_single = st.button(\"Analyze\", type=\"primary\", width='stretch', key=\"btn_tw_single\")\r\n\r\n    if do_single or st.session_state.get('tw_analyzed', False):\r\n\r\n        if do_single:\r\n            with st.spinner(f\"Analyzing {single_code}...\"):\r\n                r = analyze(single_code, \"TW\")\r\n            st.session_state['tw_analyzed'] = True\r\n        elif 'single_result' in st.session_state:\r\n            r = st.session_state['single_result']\r\n        else:\r\n            r = None\r\n\r\n        if r:\r\n\r\n            st.session_state['single_result'] = r\r\n            bd = r.get('score_breakdown', {})\r\n\r\n            # ═══════════════════════════════════════\r\n            #  ACTION BAR\r\n            # ═══════════════════════════════════════\r\n            score = r['score']\r\n            tier  = r['tier']\r\n            rsi_v = r['rsi']\r\n            bb_v  = r['bb_pct']\r\n            macd_v = r['macd_hist']\r\n            ma_bull = r['ma20_above_ma60']\r\n            kd_ok   = r['kd_golden']\r\n\r\n            pos = (kd_ok*200)+(ma_bull*150)+((35<=rsi_v<=60)*100)+((macd_v>0)*140)+((20<=bb_v<=80)*100)\r\n            pct = min(100, max(0, int(pos*100/690)))\r\n            bar = \"█\"*(pct//10) + \"░\"*(10-pct//10)\r\n\r\n            if kd_ok and ma_bull and macd_v>0 and rsi_v<65:\r\n                act,col,trend = \"強力买入\",\"green\",\"多頭\"\r\n            elif score>=700 and rsi_v<70:\r\n                act,col,trend = \"买入\",\"blue\",\"多頭\"\r\n            elif score>=400:\r\n                act,col,trend = \"觀望\",\"gray\",\"中性\"\r\n            elif rsi_v>80 or bb_v>90:\r\n                act,col,trend = \"過熱觀望\",\"orange\",\"警覺\"\r\n            else:\r\n                act,col,trend = \"減持\",\"red\",\"空頭\"\r\n\r\n            st.markdown(\r\n                f\"<big><b>「{r['code']} {r['name'][:8]}」</b></big>\"\r\n                f\"&nbsp;&nbsp;Score {score}\"\r\n                f\"&nbsp;&nbsp;<b>:color[{col}][{bar} {act}]</b>\"\r\n                f\"&nbsp;&nbsp;{trend}趨勢\",\r\n                unsafe_allow_html=True)\r\n\r\n            # ── Signal Badges ──\r\n            sigs = []\r\n            if r['kd_golden']:      sigs.append((\"KD Golden\",\"green\"))\r\n            if r['ma20_above_ma60']: sigs.append((\"MA Bull\",\"green\"))\r\n            if r['macd_hist']>0:    sigs.append((\"MACD+\",\"green\"))\r\n            if r['bb_pct']<20:     sigs.append((\"BB Oversold\",\"blue\"))\r\n            if r['bb_pct']>80:     sigs.append((\"BB Overbought\",\"red\"))\r\n            if r['rsi']<35:         sigs.append((\"RSI Oversold\",\"blue\"))\r\n            if r['rsi']>70:         sigs.append((\"RSI Overbought\",\"red\"))\r\n            if r['vol_ratio']>2.0: sigs.append((\"Vol Surge\",\"orange\"))\r\n\r\n\n[916 more lines in file. Use offset=1900 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778601055143}}
{"type":"message","id":"8f836d8a","parentId":"abf388d9","timestamp":"2026-05-12T15:50:59.844Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the single stock deep analysis section already has a pretty good display. Let me look at the rest of it and see where I can add the metric-card HTML. Let me also look at the st.metric() calls for individual metrics.","thinkingSignature":"ef362aea73d4e8e130b4eb3ebcadcc98407ad5da8fc7df685f8f214589f32b97"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_c8ths3sm8xhr_1","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":60,"offset":1900,"path":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\\streamlit_tw_stock.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":979,"output":116,"cacheRead":99424,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":100519,"cost":{"input":0.0002937,"output":0.0001392,"cacheRead":0.00596544,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00639834}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778601055147,"responseId":"06527f62a999b4a4493b36a0148d0c71"}}
{"type":"message","id":"47bd0b54","parentId":"8f836d8a","timestamp":"2026-05-12T15:50:59.858Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_c8ths3sm8xhr_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"            if sigs:\r\n                tags = \"  \".join([f\":{c}[{l}]\" for l,c in sigs])\r\n                st.markdown(tags)\r\n            else:\r\n                st.caption(\"No signals\")\r\n\r\n            # ── Row 1: Price + RSI + K/D + BB% ──\r\n            c1,c2,c3,c4 = st.columns(4)\r\n            c1.metric(\"Price\", f\"${r['price']:.2f}\", f\"{r['chg']:+.2f}%\")\r\n            rsi_delta = rsi_v-50\r\n            if rsi_v>70:       rsi_st = \"過熱\"\r\n            elif rsi_v<35:    rsi_st = \"超賣\"\r\n            else:              rsi_st = f\"正常 {rsi_v:.0f}\"\r\n            c2.metric(\"RSI\", f\"{rsi_v:.0f}\", f\"{rsi_delta:+.0f}\", help=f\"Status: {rsi_st}\")\r\n\r\n            k_val,d_val = r['k'],r['d']\r\n            kd_lbl = \"Golden!\" if kd_ok else f\"{k_val:.0f}/{d_val:.0f}\"\r\n            c3.metric(\"K/D\", kd_lbl, f\"{k_val-d_val:+.0f}\", help=\"K above D=bullish\")\r\n\r\n            bb_delta = bb_v-50\r\n            if bb_v<20:       bb_st = \"超賣\"\r\n            elif bb_v>80:     bb_st = \"過熱\"\r\n            else:             bb_st = f\"中立 {bb_v:.0f}%\"\r\n            c4.metric(\"BB%\", f\"{bb_v:.0f}%\", f\"{bb_delta:+.0f}\", help=f\"Status: {bb_st}\")\r\n\r\n            # ── Row 2: MA20 vs MA60 + MACD + Vol + BIAS ──\r\n            d1,d2,d3,d4 = st.columns(4)\r\n            ma_diff = r['ma20']-r['ma60'] if r.get('ma60') else 0\r\n            ma_lbl = \"MA Bull\" if ma_bull else \"MA Bear\"\r\n            d1.metric(\"MA20 vs MA60\", ma_lbl, f\"{ma_diff:+.1f}\" if r.get('ma60') else \"N/A\")\r\n\r\n            d2.metric(\"MACD Hist\", f\"{macd_v:+.2f}\", f\"{macd_v:+.2f}\")\r\n\r\n            vol_v = r['vol_ratio']\r\n            vol_st = \"高量\" if vol_v>1.5 else \"低量\" if vol_v<0.8 else \"正常\"\r\n            d3.metric(\"Vol Ratio\", f\"{vol_v:.1f}x\", help=f\"Status: {vol_st}\")\r\n\r\n            bias_v = r['bias5']\r\n            bias_st = \"偏離大\" if abs(bias_v)>3 else \"正常\"\r\n            d4.metric(\"BIAS5\", f\"{bias_v:+.1f}%\", help=f\"Status: {bias_st}\")\r\n\r\n            # ── Score Breakdown (color-coded inline) ──\r\n            bd = r.get('score_breakdown', {})\r\n            items = [\r\n                ('RSI',  bd.get('rsi',0),  (35<=rsi_v<=60)),\r\n                ('MACD', bd.get('macd',0), (macd_v>0)),\r\n                ('K',    bd.get('k',0),    kd_ok),\r\n                ('D',    bd.get('d',0),    not kd_ok),\r\n                ('BB',   bd.get('bb',0),   (20<=bb_v<=80)),\r\n                ('MA',   bd.get('ma',0),   ma_bull),\r\n                ('Vol',  bd.get('vol',0),  (0.8<=vol_v<=1.5)),\r\n            ]\r\n            sb_parts = []\r\n            for k,v,good in items:\r\n                color = 'green' if good else 'gray'\r\n                sb_parts.append(f\":{color}[{k} {v}]\")\r\n            st.markdown(\"  \".join(sb_parts))\r\n\r\n            # ── 📊 Technical Detail Button ──\r\n            detail_key = f\"detail_{single_code}\"\r\n\n[856 more lines in file. Use offset=1960 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778601059858}}
{"type":"message","id":"ba6054fe","parentId":"47bd0b54","timestamp":"2026-05-12T15:51:06.319Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the current Single Stock Deep Analysis section. It already has:- `st.metric()` calls for Price, RSI, K/D, BB%- Row 2 metrics for MA, MACD, Vol, BIAS\n- Score breakdown with color-coded inline elementsWhat the v3.1 example adds is a **metric-card HTML div** instead of just st.metric. Let me look at what the v3.1 example shows for the deep analysis card:```python\nst.markdown(f\"\"\"\n <div class=\"metric-card\">\n <h2>{target_code} 分析報告</h2>\n <p>評級: <span style=\"font-size:24px; color:#1E88E5; font-weight:bold;\">{r['tier']}</span> |\n 得分: <b>{r['score']}</b></p>\n <hr>\n <p>RSI: {r['rsi']:.1f} | 漲跌: {r['chg']:.2f}%</p>\n <p>Vegas 訊號: <span style=\"color:{r['v_col']}; font-weight:bold;\">{r['vegas']} ({r['v_bias']})</span></p>\n </div>\n \"\"\", unsafe_allow_html=True)\n```\n\nI should add a metric-card HTML div at the top of the deep analysis section. But I need to be careful not to break the existing metrics layout. Maybe I should add it after the action bar markdown but before the metrics rows. Actually, looking at the v3.1 example, the metric-card is a single card replacing the metrics. In the current implementation, metrics are already well-organized in columns.\n\n\nI'll add a visual summary card after the action bar to highlight the key metrics before diving into the detailed columns. This should integrate well with the existing structure without causing conflicts.","thinkingSignature":"99add640e4565aed60bd82a0125f633bde7a4ee306af10513b00b30c6841fe63"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8s3fk102qkoy_1","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":20,"offset":1878,"path":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\\streamlit_tw_stock.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1060,"output":455,"cacheRead":100384,"cacheWrite