{"type":"message","id":"8d6a2064","parentId":"254d9b44","timestamp":"2026-05-12T15:51:39.219Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now let me update the plan and report on what's been done and what's remaining. The toast notifications have been added. The deeper sidebar refactoring (replacing `col_side` with `st.sidebar`) is complex because it would require restructuring the form logic. Let me keep that as pending and report clearly.","thinkingSignature":"fde3bb4a7e63bb6252310f6127f3e2972b62e6874761d3521b06d5bf02117771"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gfd7jcklptry_1","name":"update_plan","arguments":{"plan":[{"status":"completed","step":"1. 更新 page title 為 v3.1"},{"status":"completed","step":"2. CSS metric-card 增強（已加入）"},{"status":"completed","step":"3. 加入 st.toast 通知（掃描完成 + Telegram 發送）"},{"status":"in_progress","step":"4. st.sidebar 側邊欄改造（複雜，需重構 form 邏輯）"},{"status":"pending","step":"5. 個股分析卡片化（HTML/CSS）"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":129,"output":218,"cacheRead":102656,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":103003,"cost":{"input":0.0000387,"output":0.00026159999999999996,"cacheRead":0.006159359999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.006459659999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778601093190,"responseId":"06527f87884b90d87c895f00f8b49b23"}}
