{"type":"message","id":"8c8c6739","parentId":"55430ec0","timestamp":"2026-05-12T15:51:47.392Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The sidebar restructuring (step 4) is complex because it involves moving the filter form out of the tab and into the sidebar, and restructuring the col_side/col_main layout. That's a significant refactor.\n\nFor now, let me let Jo know what I've done and check the download progress. The remaining items (sidebar restructuring and HTML metric cards) are more invasive changes that would need careful testing.\n","thinkingSignature":"df4096452997740e293d6aeec3d317e49e626c463820b00f794ae10502fc945a"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n✅ **已完成 B 方案第一波 UI 移植並推送**\n\n**變更：**\n1. ✅ Page title → `v3.1`\n2. ✅ CSS metric-card 樣式\n3. ✅ `st.toast` 通知 — 每次掃描完成 + Telegram 發送成功\n4. ⏳ st.sidebar 側邊欄改造（需要重構 `col_side/col_main` 邏輯）\n5. ⏳ 個股分析 HTML 卡片化（`st.markdown` 已經有相當好的呈現）\n\n**現有 UI 其實已經很不錯了** — 分級彩色信號標籤 + Progress bar + 6欄 Market Overview + 4欄技術指標。側邊欄搬遷風險高，回報有限。\n\n---\n\n**Qwen3.5 下載：**\n- ~312 MB / 2,741 MB，進行中（約 12%）\n- 速度 1-2 MB/s，預估還需 25+ 分鐘\n\n要繼續做側邊欄重構嗎？還是先等下載完成專注在 Qwen3.5 安裝？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":201,"output":324,"cacheRead":102752,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":103277,"cost":{"input":0.000060299999999999995,"output":0.00038879999999999996,"cacheRead":0.00616512,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00661422}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778601099231,"responseId":"06527f8f9d0aeac9dcef872d0f2054f3"}}
