{"type":"message","id":"5f0af70c","parentId":"ada390a2","timestamp":"2026-05-12T15:52:51.361Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_u4rrale8sgii_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\r\n# ═══════════════════════════ TW TAB ═══════════════════════════\r\n\r\nwith tw_tab:\r\n\r\n    col_side, col_main = st.columns([1, 4], vertical_alignment=\"top\")\r\n\r\n    with col_side:\r\n\r\n        st.header(\"Filters\")\r\n\r\n        tw_cat = st.selectbox(\"Category\", list(TW_CATS.keys()), key=\"tw_cat\")\r\n\r\n        with st.form(key=\"grade_filter_tw\"):\r\n            st.markdown(\"**評級**\")\r\n            g1, g2, g3, g4, gall = st.columns([1,1,1,1,1])\r\n            g_a = g1.checkbox(\"A\", value=True, key=\"tw_grade_a\")\r\n            g_b = g2.checkbox(\"B\", value=True, key=\"tw_grade_b\")\r\n            g_c = g3.checkbox(\"C\", value=True, key=\"tw_grade_c\")\r\n            g_d = g4.checkbox(\"D\", value=True, key=\"tw_grade_d\")\r\n            if gall.form_submit_button(\"全\", help=\"Select All\", width='stretch'):\r\n                pass  # Checkbox values are auto-managed by Streamlit via key=\r\n            tw_grade = [g for g, on in zip([\"A\",\"B\",\"C\",\"D\"], [g_a, g_b, g_c, g_d]) if on]\r\n\r\n        tw_score_min = st.slider(\"Score Min\", 0, 1000, 0, key=\"tw_score\")\r\n        tw_rsi_max = st.slider(\"RSI Max\", 30, 100, 100, key=\"tw_rsi\")\r\n\r\n        tw_macd_filter = st.checkbox(\"排除 MACD < 0\", value=False, key=\"tw_macd_filter\")\r\n\r\n        codes = TW_CATS.get(tw_cat, [])\r\n\r\n        st.info(f\"{len(codes)} stocks\")\r\n\r\n        analyze_tw = st.button(\"Analyze\", type=\"primary\", width='stretch', key=\"btn_tw_analyze\")\r\n        _log.info(\"[UI] TW Analyze button ready\")\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n    if 'tw_results' not in st.session_state:\r\n\r\n        st.session_state.tw_results = None\r\n\r\n        st.session_state.tw_filtered = None\r\n\r\n        st.session_state.tw_cat_saved = None\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n    if analyze_tw:\r\n\r\n        with st.spinner(\"Analyzing + Fetching Institutional...\"):\r\n\r\n            def _analyze_one(idx_code):\r\n\r\n                i, code = idx_code\r\n\r\n                return i, analyze(code, 'TW')\r\n\r\n            results = []\r\n\r\n\n[1254 more lines in file. Use offset=1568 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778601171361}}
{"type":"message","id":"ee58a6e0","parentId":"5f0af70c","timestamp":"2026-05-12T15:52:57.770Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture of the sidebar structure. Let me write the report.\n\nCurrent sidebar structure:\n- Lines 1511-1541: `col_side` with:\n  - `st.header(\"Filters\")`\n  - `tw_cat = st.selectbox(\"Category\", list(TW_CATS.keys()), key=\"tw_cat\")`\n  - `with st.form(key=\"grade_filter_tw\")`: 5 checkboxes + \"全\" button\n  - `tw_score_min = st.slider(\"Score Min\", 0, 1000, 0, key=\"tw_score\")`\n  - `tw_rsi_max = st.slider(\"RSI Max\", 30, 100, 100, key=\"tw_rsi\")`\n  - `tw_macd_filter = st.checkbox(\"排除 MACD < 0\", value=False, key=\"tw_macd_filter\")`\n  - `st.info(f\"{len(codes)} stocks\")`\n  - `analyze_tw = st.button(\"Analyze\", type=\"primary\", width='stretch', key=\"btn_tw_analyze\")`\n\nThe critical issue is that `with st.form()` blocks widget state updates until the form is submitted, but Streamlit requires user interaction with form elements to update session state properly. The `Analyze` button sits inside `col_side`, which limits how it can be positioned relative to other controls. Moving to `st.sidebar` would require restructuring this entire block, since sidebar widgets behave differently with form submission and layout positioning.\n\nI should verify whether the download is still running before proceeding with the migration.","thinkingSignature":"df7ba311a5d103d7cd47673b21a227b8f8119e7a2c07dfa4ce979f430e97928e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ge00g2fb5kwu_1","name":"process","arguments":{"action":"poll","sessionId":"quick-wharf","timeout":3000}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":663,"output":375,"cacheRead":107744,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":108782,"cost":{"input":0.00019889999999999998,"output":0.00045,"cacheRead":0.00646464,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00711354}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778601171364,"re