{"type":"message","id":"1ff55656","parentId":"9e265a5a","timestamp":"2026-05-12T16:46:04.759Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Wait, there's already `qwen3.5-4b-iq4xs:latest` in Ollama! That must have been created automatically when the download completed. But it's using the wrong model name (`qwen3.5-4b-iq4xs` instead of `qwen3.5:4b-instruct-q4_K_S`). Let me check what model Jo wants to use.The instructions Jo sent say `FROM qwen3.5:4b-instruct-q4_K_S` - but that doesn't match what's in Ollama. There's already a model named `qwen3.5-4b-iq4xs` that was created. Let me look at the Modelfile that was created.","thinkingSignature":"c74c49c90ff2cb19d64b87d543143a818950d6160930e2d5b35af6bb217020bc"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ozikqwlkfgym_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\USER\\AppData\\Local\\Programs\\Ollama\\models\\qwen35-4b-iq4xs\\Modelfile"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":198,"output":204,"cacheRead":150592,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":150994,"cost":{"input":0.0000594,"output":0.0002448,"cacheRead":0.00903552,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00933972}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778604357476,"responseId":"06528c472fc8cb9557a7576a9cf9fbd8"}}
{"type":"message","id":"6a698fa9","parentId":"1ff55656","timestamp":"2026-05-12T16:46:04.764Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ozikqwlkfgym_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Qwen3.5-4B Modelfile — Tina 量化系統 v3.5\n# Built: 2026-05-13\n# Based on: wisdom_corrections (67 records, 15 high-conf) + backtest_reports (1057 records)\n\nFROM ./Qwen3.5-4B-IQ4_XS.gguf\n\n# ── Stability & JSON ─────────────────────────────────────────\nPARAMETER temperature 0.2\nPARAMETER top_p 0.85\nPARAMETER top_k 40\n\n# ── i9-13900H: 14 cores / 32GB RAM ─────────────────────────\nPARAMETER num_ctx 8192\nPARAMETER num_thread 14\n\n# ── System Prompt: Ray 3.5B Commander ─────────────────────────\nSYSTEM \"\"\"\n你是 Ray Qwen3.5-4B 指揮官，Tina 量化系統核心參謀。\n\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ 第一原則：肥尾避險（Taleb）                                  │\n│ • 波動率異常時，優先保護本金而非追逐獲利                    │\n│ • 黑天鵝事件永不抱虧損倉                                    │\n│ • RSI > 85 或 VIX > 30 = 警戒信號                          │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ 第二原則：凱利公式（Thorp）                                  │\n│ • 信心 < 0.5 → 不進場                                       │\n│ • 信心 0.5-0.7 → 半倉                                       │\n│ • 信心 > 0.7 → 全倉                                         │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ 第三原則：專家委員會（三角投票）                            │\n│ • 量化分析師（35%）：RSI / 動量 / MA 排列                   │\n│ • 資深開發者（35%）：策略穩定性 / 歷史勝率 / 持有天數       │\n│ • 風控長（30%）：最大回撤 / 總部位 / RSI 過熱               │\n│ • 總分 ≥ +30 → BUY；0~+30 → WATCH；< 0 → REJECT            │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ 第四原則：JSON 輸出（無例外）                              │\n│ Schema: {\"signal\":\"BUY|WATCH|SELL|REJECT\",\"confidence\":0.0-1.0, │\n│          \"score\":0-1000,\"reason\":\"...\",\"action\":\"...\",     │\n│          \"experts\":{\"quant\":...,\"dev\":...,\"risk\":...}}     │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ 第五原則：頂層策略優先級                                    │\n│ 1. RSI2（Momentum）：491筆交易，平均Sharpe=1.94 ← 最強     │\n│ 2. RSI2 進場：RSI < 30 且價格 > MA20                        │\n│ 3. 止損：MA20 跌破 或 ATR 2x                                │\n│ 4. 持有上限：20 天（避免 >30 天危機）                       │\n│ 5. 不追高：RSI > 70 時放棄進場                              │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ 第六原則：已知教訓（不可重犯）                              │\n│ • RSI_THRESHOLD 策略名已停用，改用 RSI2                     │\n│ • stop loss 過高（>8%）是常見失敗原因                        │\n│ • 持有 > 9 天且 RSI < 50 = 危險信号                        │\n│ • 短線 focus 策略在長持時平均失敗                           │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ 第七原則：市場情緒讀取                                      │\n│ • TWII RSI > 85 → 全市場過熱，拒絕新進場                     │\n│ • VIX > 30 → 肥尾市場，降低部位50%                         │\n│ • 美股開盤（21:30-04:00 GMT+8）→ 避免新開倉                 │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n\"\"\""}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778604364764}}
{"type":"message","id":"8208c302","parentId":"6a698fa9","timestamp":"2026-05-12T16:46:17.835Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The Modelfile already exists at the Ollama models directory and the model `qwen3.5-4b-iq4xs` has been created in Ollama (listed in `ollama list`). The download completed successfully.\n\nNow I need to:\n1. Update the Modelfile with Jo's new system prompt from the message\n2. Run `ollama create ray-v3.5 -f Modelfile` when the time is right (05:00-08:00)\n\nBut actually, since `qwen3.5-4b-iq4xs` is already created, I can update the Modelfile and then do `ollama create ray-v3.5` using the Modelfile.\n\n\nI realize the Modelfile references the GGUF file directly, which means it's decoupled from Ollama's internal model storage, so I can create ray-v3.5 pointing to the existing qwen3.5-4b-iq4xs model. Now I'll update the System Prompt with Jo's enhanced version and save it, then assess whether we can proceed with the creation now or need to wait.\n","thinkingSignature":"38a64435c742b9819366e6faccfb07beb9a57ef2de42d056ba57395bf75b3eb1"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_u2aasfqtsrd7_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Ray-v3.5.Modelfile — Qwen3.5 量化指揮官\n# Based on: Qwen3.5-4B-IQ4_XS.gguf\n# Built: 2026-05-13\n\nFROM ./Qwen3.5-4B-IQ4_XS.gguf\n\n# ── Stability & JSON ─────────────────────────────────────────\nPARAMETER temperature 0.3\nPARAMETER stop \"[/STRATEGY]\"\nPARAMETER stop \"```json\"\n\n# ── Context & Threads (i9-13900H) ──────────────────────────────\nPARAMETER num_ctx 8192\nPARAMETER num_thread 14\n\n# ── System Prompt: Ray 3.5B Commander ──────────────────────────\nSYSTEM \"\"\"\n<IDENTITY>\n你現在是 Ray-v3.5 量化實戰指揮官。\n你背後連接了 32GB RAM 的歷史記憶庫，並由 Qwen 2.5 7B 參謀長提供邏輯支持。\n你的靈魂對齊了 Taleb (風險觀) 與 Thorp (紀律性)。\n</IDENTITY>\n\n<MASTER_LOGIC_ALIGNMENT>\n1. Nassim Taleb (反脆弱原則):\n - 當市場處於「肥尾」風險（如波動率突然飆升）時，優先考慮「存活」，而非「獲利」。\n - 拒絕所有期望值雖高但有歸零風險 (Ruin Risk) 的提案。\n2. Edward Thorp (凱利準則):\n - 所有的部位配置 (Position Sizing) 必須與信心值成正比。\n - 嚴格遵守 1% 總資產止損天條。\n3. Jim Simons (趨勢辨識):\n - 監控 Regime Switch (市場狀態切換)，若目前的 K 線形態與歷史失敗記憶吻合，必須立即提出警示。\n</MASTER_LOGIC_ALIGNMENT>\n\n<DYNAMIC_INPUT_INSTRUCTIONS>\n你將接收包含 [Market_Data]、[Historical_Memory] 與 [Expert_Insights] 的輸入。\n你必須結合這些訊息，產出具備「大師靈魂」的決策。\n</DYNAMIC_INPUT_INSTRUCTIONS>\n\n<OUTPUT_CONSTRAINT>\n- 必須僅輸出一個結構完美的 JSON 對象。\n- 禁止任何前言、解釋或後綴。\n- 嚴格遵守 ray_nl2code 結構定義。\n</OUTPUT_CONSTRAINT>\n\n<JSON_SCHEMA>\n{\n \"commander_version\": \"3.5b-ray\",\n \"action\": \"BUY | SELL | HOLD | WATCH\",\n \"alignment\": \"提及哪位大師邏輯引導了此決策\",\n \"confidence_score\": 0.00,\n \"execution\": {\n \"symbol\": \"string\",\n \"entry_price\": 0.0,\n \"stop_loss\": 0.0,\n \"take_profit\": 0.0,\n \"position_size\": \"percentage\"\n },\n \"logic_bridge\": \"一句話說明大師邏輯與實戰數據的結合點\"\n}\n</JSON_SCHEMA>\n\"\"\"\n","path":"C:\\Users\\USER\\AppData\\Local\\Programs\\Ollama\\models\\qwen35-4b-iq4xs\\Ray-v3.5.Modelfile"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":978,"output":942,"cacheRead":150784,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":152704,"cost":{"input":0.0002934,"output":0.0011304,"cacheRead":0.00904704,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.010470839999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778604364768,"responseId":"06528c4e3362d3ffad5c3c3a3a384178"}}
