{"type":"message","id":"af8f84f9","parentId":"fc750004","timestamp":"2026-05-12T16:49:20.459Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_mjdxqdmout8x_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"llm_router.py:83:        \"\"\"Layer 1: 快速策略提案（走 ray-v1）\"\"\"\r\nllm_router.py:121:            # 降級到 ray-v1"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":192,"aggregated":"llm_router.py:83:        \"\"\"Layer 1: 快速策略提案（走 ray-v1）\"\"\"\r\nllm_router.py:121:            # 降級到 ray-v1","cwd":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778604560459}}
{"type":"message","id":"b2827a6f","parentId":"af8f84f9","timestamp":"2026-05-12T16:49:25.064Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me look at llm_router.py more carefully to understand the model references.","thinkingSignature":"3766c5eb1345505c128356167cc5f3e9b1959cded07860ea849f294f186b7bda"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xo7hb0g7oudn_1","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":60,"path":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\llm_router.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":148142,"output":68,"cacheRead":15749,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":163959,"cost":{"input":0.0444426,"output":0.00008159999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0009449399999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.04546914}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778604560462,"responseId":"06528d12afa7e8b6409be17e56a4c91e"}}
{"type":"message","id":"76543f52","parentId":"b2827a6f","timestamp":"2026-05-12T16:49:25.071Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_xo7hb0g7oudn_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-\n\"\"\"\nLLM Router - 統一調度層\n=======================\n所有 LLM 調用必須經過這裡，禁止跨層直接 call Ollama。\n\n分層原則：\n  Layer 0: 純本地計算 → 不走 LLM（ray_engine.py, us_momentum.py 等）\n  Layer 1: 快速策略  → ray-deep-v1（Qwen 7B，Jo 全指定）\n  Layer 2: 深度推理  → MiniMax Remnant（雲端，3-15s）\n  Layer 3: 連網學習  → MiniMax（帶 web_fetch 能力）\n\n使用範例：\n  router = LLMRouter()\n  result = router.call(\"deep_analysis\", {\"data\": ...})\n\"\"\"\n\nimport os, json, time\nfrom typing import Dict, Any, Optional\n\n# ── MiniMax API ──────────────────────────────────────────────\nMINIMAX_API_KEY = ***\"MINIMAX_API_KEY\") or os.getenv(\"api-key\") or \"\"\nMINIMAX_BASE_URL = \"https://api.minimax.chat/v1\"\n\n# ── Ollama 本地模型映射 ─────────────────────────────────────────\n# 優先順序（根據速度和品質平衡）\n# Layer 1: 快速任務\nLOCAL_MODEL_FAST   = \"ray-deep-v1\"        # Qwen 7B (4.7GB) - Jo 指定全本地分析走 ray-deep\n\n# Layer 2: 深度任務\nLOCAL_MODEL_DEEP   = \"ray-deep-v1\"       # Qwen 7B - 與 fast 統一，Jo 全指定 ray-deep\nLOCAL_MODEL_ALT_DEEP = \"ray-deep-v1\"     # 備用同樣是 ray-deep\nLOCAL_MODEL_COMMANDER = \"ray-commander\"   # ray-deep-v1 + 大師對齊 System Prompt\n\n\nclass LLMRouter:\n    \"\"\"統一 LLM 調度器\"\"\"\n\n    def __init__(self):\n        self.local_fast    = LOCAL_MODEL_FAST\n        self.local_alt_fast = LOCAL_MODEL_FAST   # Jo 指定：全本地分析走 ray-deep\n        self.local_v3      = LOCAL_MODEL_FAST   # Jo 指定：V3 備用同樣是 ray-deep\n        self.local_deep    = LOCAL_MODEL_DEEP   # Jo 指定：統一走 ray-deep\n        self.local_alt_deep = LOCAL_MODEL_ALT_DEEP\n        self.local_commander = \"ray-deep-v1\"\n        self.minimax_model = \"minimax/MiniMax-M2.7\"  # MiniMax Remnant\n        self._mm_client = None\n        self._ollama_fallback_chain = [\n            # Layer 1 fallback chain\n            (LOCAL_MODEL_FAST,     30, 0.1),\n            (LOCAL_MODEL_ALT_FAST, 30, 0.1),\n            (LOCAL_MODEL_V3,       45, 0.15),\n            # Layer 2 fallback chain\n            (LOCAL_MODEL_DEEP,     300, 0.2),\n            (LOCAL_MODEL_ALT_DEEP, 300, 0.2),\n        ]\n\n    # ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\n    # 公開 API\n    # ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\n\n[241 more lines in file. Use offset=61 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778604565071}}
{"type":"message","id":"9f7b46bf","parentId":"76543f52","timestamp":"2026-05-12T16:49:33.533Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see - all local models are already pointing to `ray-deep-v1`. But I need to update `LOCAL_MODEL_FAST` and related to point to `ray-v3.5` since that's the new 4B commander. However, the system prompt is different for 4B vs 7B.\n\nActually, looking at Jo's design:\n- 4B (ray-v3.5): Fast execution during trading hours\n- 7B (ray-deep-v1): Deep analysis during training hours\n\nSo I should update `LOCAL_MODEL_FAST` to `ray-v3.5`, and keep `LOCAL_MODEL_DEEP` as `ray-deep-v1`.\n\n\nLet me verify the current state of these model assignments.","thinkingSignature":"8d58e5b4f8795a1603aade4fd1cc1af88151de63f7b5e3902b1629a11d440eab"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_uuptlozjaa62_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python -c \"\nfrom importlib import import_module, reload\nimport sys\nsys.path.insert(0, r'C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray')\nimport llm_router\nreload(llm_router)\nr = llm_router.LLMRouter()\nprint('local_fast:', r.local_fast)\nprint('local_deep:', r.local_deep)\nprint('local_v3:', r.local_v3)\n\"","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":148929,"output":274,"cacheRead":15749,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":164952,"cost":{"input":0.044678699999999995,"output":0.00032879999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0009449399999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.04595243999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778604565074,"responseId":"06528d17f299000376fba92dcbc984f6"}}
