{"type":"message","id":"e4f05809","parentId":"363533aa","timestamp":"2026-05-12T16:51:13.532Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now let me set up the cron jobs for the training pipeline:\n1. 14:00 - Phase 1: 7B distills 144 wisdom_corrections\n2. 17:00 - Phase 2: 7B injects master logic into Modelfile\n3. 05:00 - Phase 3: ollama create ray-v3.5 ✅ already done\n\nAlso, I need to commit and push all the changes (llm_router.py, ray_scheduler.py, master_axioms.json).\n\nLet me set up the two training cron jobs.","thinkingSignature":"a126933bec63ef5ccd22d8bf4256f109b26668b7ba7a8d17efa3f31df35db0c1"},{"type":"text","text":"Router 修復。現在一口氣設定 Phase 1 & 2 的 cron job 並 commit push：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_dnpv8vfsd12k_1","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"add","job":{"name":"Phase1: 7B 蒸餾 144 筆失敗歸因 → 10大禁止規則","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"=== Phase 1: 邏輯蒸餾 (14:00-17:00) ===\n\n執行 ray_logic_distiller.py：\n1. 讀取 ray_wisdom.db 中所有 wisdom_corrections（67筆）\n2. 呼叫 ollama（ray-deep-v1）將失敗案例蒸餾成 10 條「絕對禁止行為」\n3. 格式：If [指標條件] Then [禁止行動]\n4. 產出：ray_forbidden_rules.json\n\n範例輸出格式：\n[\n  {\"rule\": \"If RSI>80 AND 外資轉賣 Then 嚴禁持有多單\", \"master\": \"Taleb\"},\n  {\"rule\": \"If 持有天數>9 AND RSI<50 Then 立即止損\", \"master\": \"Thorp\"}\n]\n\n完成後 commit push","timeoutSeconds":600},"schedule":{"expr":"0 14 * * *","kind":"cron","tz":"Asia/Taipei"},"sessionTarget":"isolated"}}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":31164,"output":460,"cacheRead":15749,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47373,"cost":{"input":0.0093492,"output":0.000552,"cacheRead":0.0009449399999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01084614}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778604665201,"responseId":"06528d7a6be829d4ca7054ed55326ba8"}}
