\\n\\\\n直接執行：python C:\\\\\\\\Users\\\\\\\\USER\\\\\\\\.openclaw\\\\\\\\workspace\\\\\\\\Tina_Quant_System\\\\\\\\stores\\\\\\\\cron_governor.py\\\\n\\\\n功能：\\\\n1. 讀取 cron_governor_state.json\\\\n2. 計算系統活動分數（0-100）\\\\n3. 如果 score < 30 且在 02:00-06:00，執行深夜喚醒 jobs\\\\n4. 更新 cron_governor_state.json\\\\n\\\\n限時：90秒\\\\n\\\\n⚠️ 只做監控和決策，不實際執行 jobs\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 90\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"none\",\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"1616824689\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1778605471697,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1778601873223,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 42913,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-requested\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"consecutiveSkipped\": 0\n      },\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1778601916136\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"d824a2bb-a4ba-4d6f-8119-9e7b945deb6e\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"name\": \"Tina 自主決策五大層\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1778216986278,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"anchorMs\": 1778250957278,\n        \"everyMs\": 10800000,\n        \"kind\": \"every\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"【Tina Cron v2 — 五大層全面升級版】\\n\\n執行：python C:\\\\Users\\\\USER\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\Tina_Quant_System\\\\scripts\\\\tina_cron_v2.py\\n\\n這會：\\n1. Layer 1 目標追蹤（部位% / 月報酬 / 年度目標）\\n2. Layer 2 風控（TWII RSI >75/80/85/90 分級行動）\\n3. Layer 3 持倉計時器（持有天數 / 移動停損 / 到目標距離 / RSI現值）\\n4. Layer 4 市場（TWII RSI + MA20/60 排列 + VIX + 法人流向 + 市場情緒分）\\n5. Layer 5 行動分級（★★★ BUY / ★★ BUY / WATCH / REDUCE / SELL）\\n\\n結果寫入：stores/short_term/tina_cron_v2_output.json\\n\\n限時：120秒\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 300\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"none\",\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"1616