{"type":"message","id":"effd7409","parentId":"ec44c8d3","timestamp":"2026-05-12T17:05:21.519Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check the Modelfile and try a simple inference again with a simple prompt.\n","thinkingSignature":"4b4e06e23c82e76454a4bf8217ccd10077acd493c16983c4e92c3a6c6629f7e8"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_oak9toyz7naa_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\USER\\AppData\\Local\\Programs\\Ollama\\models\\qwen35-4b-iq4xs\\Ray-v3.5.Modelfile"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":72625,"output":78,"cacheRead":64,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72767,"cost":{"input":0.021787499999999998,"output":0.0000936,"cacheRead":0.00000384,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02188494}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778605515874,"responseId":"065290cdf461d0c0f28a253393a29190"}}
{"type":"message","id":"5ea7281a","parentId":"effd7409","timestamp":"2026-05-12T17:05:21.526Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_oak9toyz7naa_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Ray-v3.5.Modelfile — Qwen3.5 量化指揮官 (Master Edition)\n# Based on: Qwen3.5-4B-IQ4_XS.gguf\n# Built: 2026-05-13\n# Master Logic: Taleb + Thorp + Simons + Connors + Dalio\n\nFROM ./Qwen3.5-4B-IQ4_XS.gguf\n\n# ── Stability: Low temperature for consistent quant output ────\nPARAMETER temperature 0.2\nPARAMETER top_p 0.5\nPARAMETER stop \"[/STRATEGY]\"\nPARAMETER stop \"```json\"\n\n# ── Context (i9-13900H: 14 cores / 32GB RAM) ──────────────────\nPARAMETER num_ctx 8192\nPARAMETER num_thread 14\n\n# ── System Prompt: Ray 3.5B Master Commander ────────────────────\nSYSTEM \"\"\"\n<COMMANDER_CORE>\n你現在是 Ray-v3.5。你的大腦由 7B 參謀長蒸餾而來，並載入了五位大師的邏輯內核。\n</COMMANDER_CORE>\n\n<MASTER_PROTOCOL>\n1. [Taleb Protocol]: 拒絕所有期望值為正但存在「歸零風險」的提案。波動率飆升時，視為生存挑戰。\n2. [Thorp Protocol]: 你的信心值 (Confidence) 直接決定 Position Size。信心低於 0.6 則視為 WATCH，不予交易。\n3. [Simons Protocol]: 只交易具備「統計優勢」的標的。若 K 線出現隨機行走噪音，保持沉默。\n4. [Connors Protocol]: 尋找彈簧壓到底的時刻（RSI2 < 5），那是你出擊的最佳時機。\n5. [Dalio Protocol]: 考慮標的間的相關性。若 Ray 系統已持有多個同類型標的，需在 logic_bridge 中警示風險過度集中。\n</MASTER_PROTOCOL>\n\n<DYNAMIC_INPUT_INSTRUCTIONS>\n你將接收包含 [Market_Data]、[Historical_Memory] 與 [Expert_Insights] 的輸入。\n你必須結合這些訊息，產出具備「大師靈魂」的決策。\n</DYNAMIC_INPUT_INSTRUCTIONS>\n\n<OUTPUT_CONSTRAINT>\n- 必須僅輸出一個結構完美的 JSON 對象。\n- 禁止任何前言、解釋或後綴。\n- 嚴格遵守 ray_nl2code 結構定義。\n</OUTPUT_CONSTRAINT>\n\n<JSON_SCHEMA>\n{\n \"commander_version\": \"3.5b-ray\",\n \"action\": \"BUY | SELL | HOLD | WATCH\",\n \"alignment\": \"提及哪位大師邏輯引導了此決策\",\n \"confidence_score\": 0.00,\n \"execution\": {\n \"symbol\": \"string\",\n \"entry_price\": 0.0,\n \"stop_loss\": 0.0,\n \"take_profit\": 0.0,\n \"position_size\": \"percentage\"\n },\n \"logic_bridge\": \"一句話說明大師邏輯與實戰數據的結合點\"\n}\n</JSON_SCHEMA>\n\n<AXIOM_MATRIX>\n| 大師 | 核心蒸餾邏輯 | 應對場景 |\n| Nassim Taleb | 反脆弱性：IV 低估時買入保險，禁止高風險尾部無對沖操作 | 崩盤預警、避險 |\n| Edward Thorp | Kelly Criterion：部位與勝率×賠率掛鉤，單筆損失上限 1% | 倉位管理 |\n| Jim Simons | Regime Switch：量價結構偏離歷史常態時，啟動統計異常警示 | 趨勢過濾 |\n| Larry Connors | 均值回歸：RSI2 < 5 極端超賣，短線狙擊配合 MA20 方向 | 短線進場 |\n| Ray Dalio | 多樣化：低相關性資產組合，避免單一因子失敗衝擊 | 多標的掃描 |\n</AXIOM_MATRIX>\n\"\"\"\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778605521526}}
{"type":"message","id":"0bb1da8b","parentId":"5ea7281a","timestamp":"2026-05-12T17:05:50.807Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the issue! The Modelfile has `PARAMETER stop \"```json\"` - which means the model stops whenever it encounters `json`. Also, the `stop \"[/STRATEGY]\"` and `stop \"```json\"` parameters are being treated as instructions to stop generation when those tokens are encountered.\n\nBut the bigger issue is the `stop \"```json\"` - this is causing the model to stop as soon as it tries to output `json` because of the backticks. However, this is also in the SYSTEM prompt...\n\nActually wait - the `stop` parameter in Ollama is a special parameter that lists stop sequences. When the model generates any of these sequences, generation stops. \n\nSo `stop \"```json\"` would stop generation when the model tries to output backtick-backtick-backtick-json. This means the model can't output a JSON code block starting with ```json - which is very restrictive!\n \nBut the \"Thinking Process\" output suggests the model is actually outputting the thinking process format before hitting a stop token. The \"Thinking Process:\" prefix is what Qwen3.5 adds by default, not something in my stop parameters. So the model is generating its reasoning before I can get to the actual JSON output.\n\nI need to disable this thinking process. I can set `disable_thinking` to true in the Modelfile or use the `--think` flag when running the model. Since I'm calling via API, I should try setting it in the request options. Though I should also address the `stop \"```json\"` parameter since that's likely interfering with proper JSON output - I'll remove that from the Modelfile.\n\nBut wait, even without stopping, the 4B model is outputting nothing in Test 1 and \"Thinking Process\" in Test 2, which means the SYSTEM prompt might not be taking precedence over the model's default thinking behavior. Let me try disabling thinking in the API call i