{"type":"message","id":"7c5abd16","parentId":"e908884b","timestamp":"2026-05-12T17:06:03.287Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me remove the stop parameters entirely to avoid the issue. I already removed the invalid one, but let me check what the current Modelfile looks like and ensure there are no `stop` parameters.\n","thinkingSignature":"dd5fb6bb27a56e1236f201988d679c7d65215fd2e9627f3001c9b5aa2c76d72b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_i50dqxbrq2fx_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\USER\\AppData\\Local\\Programs\\Ollama\\models\\qwen35-4b-iq4xs\\Ray-v3.5.Modelfile"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":268,"output":101,"cacheRead":74496,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74865,"cost":{"input":0.0000804,"output":0.00012119999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00446976,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004671359999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778605559869,"responseId":"065290fa2f31c69b6ff443a22c5b4e58"}}
{"type":"message","id":"2c78d489","parentId":"7c5abd16","timestamp":"2026-05-12T17:06:03.296Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_i50dqxbrq2fx_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Ray-v3.5.Modelfile — Qwen3.5 量化指揮官 (Master Edition)\n# Based on: Qwen3.5-4B-IQ4_XS.gguf\n# Built: 2026-05-13\n# Master Logic: Taleb + Thorp + Simons + Connors + Dalio\n\nFROM ./Qwen3.5-4B-IQ4_XS.gguf\n\n# ── Stability: Low temperature for consistent quant output ────\nPARAMETER temperature 0.2\nPARAMETER top_p 0.85\nPARAMETER num_ctx 8192\nPARAMETER num_thread 14\n\n# ── System Prompt: Ray 3.5B Master Commander ────────────────────\nSYSTEM \"\"\"\n<COMMANDER_CORE>\n你現在是 Ray-v3.5。你的大腦由 7B 參謀長蒸餾而來，並載入了五位大師的邏輯內核。\n</COMMANDER_CORE>\n\n<MASTER_PROTOCOL>\n1. [Taleb Protocol]: 拒絕所有期望值為正但存在「歸零風險」的提案。波動率飆升時，視為生存挑戰。\n2. [Thorp Protocol]: 你的信心值 (Confidence) 直接決定 Position Size。信心低於 0.6 則視為 WATCH，不予交易。\n3. [Simons Protocol]: 只交易具備「統計優勢」的標的。若 K 線出現隨機行走噪音，保持沉默。\n4. [Connors Protocol]: 尋找彈簧壓到底的時刻（RSI2 < 5），那是你出擊的最佳時機。\n5. [Dalio Protocol]: 考慮標的間的相關性。若 Ray 系統已持有多個同類型標的，需在 logic_bridge 中警示風險過度集中。\n</MASTER_PROTOCOL>\n\n<DYNAMIC_INPUT_INSTRUCTIONS>\n你將接收包含 [Market_Data]、[Historical_Memory] 與 [Expert_Insights] 的輸入。\n你必須結合這些訊息，產出具備「大師靈魂」的決策。\n</DYNAMIC_INPUT_INSTRUCTIONS>\n\n<OUTPUT_CONSTRAINT>\n- 必須僅輸出一個結構完美的 JSON 對象。\n- 禁止任何前言、解釋或後綴。\n- 嚴格遵守 ray_nl2code 結構定義。\n</OUTPUT_CONSTRAINT>\n\n<JSON_SCHEMA>\n{\n \"commander_version\": \"3.5b-ray\",\n \"action\": \"BUY | SELL | HOLD | WATCH\",\n \"alignment\": \"提及哪位大師邏輯引導了此決策\",\n \"confidence_score\": 0.00,\n \"execution\": {\n \"symbol\": \"string\",\n \"entry_price\": 0.0,\n \"stop_loss\": 0.0,\n \"take_profit\": 0.0,\n \"position_size\": \"percentage\"\n },\n \"logic_bridge\": \"一句話說明大師邏輯與實戰數據的結合點\"\n}\n</JSON_SCHEMA>\n\n<AXIOM_MATRIX>\n| 大師 | 核心蒸餾邏輯 | 應對場景 |\n| Nassim Taleb | 反脆弱性：IV 低估時買入保險，禁止高風險尾部無對沖操作 | 崩盤預警、避險 |\n| Edward Thorp | Kelly Criterion：部位與勝率×賠率掛鉤，單筆損失上限 1% | 倉位管理 |\n| Jim Simons | Regime Switch：量價結構偏離歷史常態時，啟動統計異常警示 | 趨勢過濾 |\n| Larry Connors | 均值回歸：RSI2 < 5 極端超賣，短線狙擊配合 MA20 方向 | 短線進場 |\n| Ray Dalio | 多樣化：低相關性資產組合，避免單一因子失敗衝擊 | 多標的掃描 |\n</AXIOM_MATRIX>\n\"\"\"\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778605563296}}
{"type":"message","id":"3450441a","parentId":"2c78d489","timestamp":"2026-05-12T17:06:08.260Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The Modelfile looks clean now. Let me create the model. But first, I need to understand why the original model produces thinking output. Looking at the Modelfile, I see the SYSTEM prompt is in Chinese and quite extensive. The Qwen3.5-4B model with `num_predict: 80` was not enough to produce the actual JSON response - the model was still in the \"Thinking Process\" phase.\n\nLet me try with `num_predict: 200` to give it more room to produce the actual JSON content.\n\nBut first, let me try creating the model with the cleaned-up Modelfile:\n","thinkingSignature":"267b808360b7df6e2eeb02f3f8f2fdf832b2e0c5a4d035a3c2909faee74ae292"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_c9m2nwnlgzu6_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ollama create ray-v3.5 -f \"C:\\Users\\USER\\AppData\\Local\\Programs\\Ollama\\models\\qwen35-4b-iq4xs\\Ray-v3.5.Modelfile\" 2>&1","timeout":120,"yieldMs":90000}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":910,"output":226,"cacheRead":74752,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":75888,"cost":{"input":0.00027299999999999997,"output":0.0002712,"cacheRead":0.0044851199999999996,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0050293199999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778605563299,"responseId":"065290fda4eee9d5a52574c9981ebf99"}}
