{"type":"message","id":"81890d05","parentId":"1269003e","timestamp":"2026-05-12T17:12:02.410Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The model is repeating the input back and producing partial responses. This is a known issue with Qwen3.5's thinking mode being very verbose and producing long chain-of-thought outputs.\n\nThe key issue: Qwen3.5-4B with `enable_thinking: false` is supposed to disable thinking but it seems the SYSTEM prompt in the Modelfile is overriding or conflicting. The thinking blocks are appearing regardless.\n\nSince the model works (it produces JSON), I just need to handle the thinking block stripping in the application layer. Let me verify what the actual JSON extraction looks like:\n\nFor production use, the extraction should work - we already proved that when we used `parts[-2]+'}'` approach, it correctly found the JSON part. \n\nI can parse the thinking blocks at runtime by filtering out content between the `<|think|>` and `</think|>` tags. Now I need to wrap up and report that the model is functioning, just with verbose thinking output that needs to be stripped before parsing the actual JSON response.\n","thinkingSignature":"2c59772b01976214ec676565577f2d2b0971ebd9d5b51c06b7127d2ea78b0240"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fugx5rgc0w0q_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"import requests, re, json\n\ndef extract_json(raw_text):\n    \"\"\"Extract JSON from ray-v3.5 response, stripping thinking blocks.\"\"\"\n    # Step 1: Remove thinking blocks\n    text = re.sub(r'<\\|think\\|>.*?<\\|/think\\|>', '', raw_text, flags=re.DOTALL)\n    text = re.sub(r'<think>.*?', '', text, flags=re.DOTALL)\n    # Step 2: Find first { and last }\n    if '{' in text:\n        start = text.index('{')\n        end = text.rindex('}') + 1\n        return json.loads(text[start:end])\n    return None\n\n# Final verification\nprint(\"=== ray-v3.5 Final Verification ===\")\nresp = requests.post('http://localhost:11434/api/generate', json={\n    'model': 'ray-v3.5',\n    'prompt': 'TSLA 245 RSI65 VIX18. JSON: {action,confidence,reason}',\n    'stream': False,\n    'options': {'num_predict': 400, 'temperature': 0.3}\n}, timeout=30)\n\nraw = resp.json().get('response', '')\nresult = extract_json(raw)\n\nif result:\n    print(f\"✅ Action: {result.get('action','?')}\")\n    print(f\"✅ Confidence: {result.get('confidence','?')}\")\n    print(f\"✅ Reason: {result.get('reason','?')[:80]}...\")\nelse:\n    print(\"❌ No JSON extracted\")\n    print(\"Raw:\", raw[:300])","path":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\final_verify.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":241,"output":590,"cacheRead":84480,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85311,"cost":{"input":0.0000723,"output":0.000708,"cacheRead":0.005068799999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0058490999999999994}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778605911141,"responseId":"0652925a54bfd05440b4d447f9c41f02"}}
