{"type":"message","id":"801ed145","parentId":"0c9b414a","timestamp":"2026-05-12T17:12:32.368Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is interesting - even qwen3.5-4b-iq4xs (the base model without a Modelfile) exhibits thinking. So thinking is baked into the base model's behavior, not controlled by Ollama parameters.\n\nThe real solution is to use the extract_json() function I built, which correctly strips thinking and extracts the JSON. This works - we've verified it.\n\nFor production use of ray-v3.5 in the router, I need to:\n1. Use the generate endpoint with prompt injection that includes the JSON schema in the prompt\n2. Parse the response with extract_json()\n3. Return the clean JSON to callers\n\n\nI tested this with TSLA market data and confirmed it works - the extract_json function successfully pulled the trading signal from the response. Now I need to update the llm_router to use this pattern consistently, and I can remove that invalid `think false` parameter from the Modelfile.\n","thinkingSignature":"87c2b4fa89721d07229acb3974e4b1a69da63c74b9483b2f068d8c21d308d576"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_q5ognmtazrrm_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"PARAMETER temperature 0.2\nPARAMETER top_p 0.85\nPARAMETER num_ctx 8192\nPARAMETER num_thread 14","oldText":"PARAMETER temperature 0.2\nPARAMETER top_p 0.85\nPARAMETER num_ctx 8192\nPARAMETER num_thread 14\nPARAMETER think false"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\USER\\AppData\\Local\\Programs\\Ollama\\models\\qwen35-4b-iq4xs\\Ray-v3.5.Modelfile"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":227,"output":337,"cacheRead":86080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86644,"cost":{"input":0.0000681,"output":0.00040439999999999996,"cacheRead":0.0051648,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0056373}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778605943466,"responseId":"0652927a215bb2aeb14fd043804dfda6"}}
{"type":"message","id":"03b8f1dd","parentId":"801ed145","timestamp":"2026-05-12T17:12:32.376Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_q5ognmtazrrm_1","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced 1 block(s) in C:\\Users\\USER\\AppData\\Local\\Programs\\Ollama\\models\\qwen35-4b-iq4xs\\Ray-v3.5.Modelfile."}],"details":{"diff":"    ...\n  9 PARAMETER temperature 0.2\n 10 PARAMETER top_p 0.85\n 11 PARAMETER num_ctx 8192\n 12 PARAMETER num_thread 14\n-13 PARAMETER think false\n 14 \n 15 # ── System Prompt: Ray 3.5B Master Commander ────────────────────\n 16 SYSTEM \"\"\"\n 17 <COMMANDER_CORE>\n    ...","firstChangedLine":13},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778605952376}}
{"type":"message","id":"5cca4bc9","parentId":"03b8f1dd","timestamp":"2026-05-12T17:12:40.407Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so Qwen3.5-4B with \"think\" parameter is not available in Ollama. The thinking is baked into the base model and can't be disabled. However, our `extract_json()` function CAN strip thinking blocks and extract clean JSON. The solution is:\n\n1. Keep ray-v3.5 as-is (with the SYSTEM prompt for structure)\n2. The router needs to handle thinking block stripping via `extract_json()`\n3. The model DOES respond with valid JSON - just wrapped in thinking\n\nLet me verify this with a proper test that uses our extraction function.Actually let me just test the FINAL clean approach with the proper extract function, and show Jo the results. The model IS working - it just produces thinking output. The `extract_json()` function already handles this.\n","thinkingSignature":"7c6cfa3e89100d627db404057ec6ea8ad8b7d2940f488ee08467212086d51526"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_dgdu9cily7tl_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-\n\"\"\"\nray_nl2code.py — JSON 提取包裝器 for Qwen3.5-4B (ray-v3.5)\n功能：自動去除 thinking block，提取乾淨 JSON\n\"\"\"\n\nimport re, json\nfrom typing import Optional\n\ndef extract_json(raw_text: str) -> Optional[dict]:\n    \"\"\"去除 thinking block，取出第一個乾淨 JSON\"\"\"\n    if not raw_text:\n        return None\n    # 去除 <|think|> blocks\n    text = re.sub(r'<\\|think\\|>.*?<\\|/think\\|>', '', raw_text, flags=re.DOTALL)\n    text = re.sub(r'<think>.*?', '', text, flags=re.DOTALL)\n    text = text.strip()\n    # 取第一個 { 到最後一个 }\n    if '{' in text:\n        start = text.index('{')\n        end = text.rindex('}') + 1\n        return json.loads(text[start:end])\n    return None\n\ndef parse_ray_response(raw: str) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"完整解析 ray-v3.5 回應\"\"\"\n    result = extract_json(raw)\n    if result:\n        return {\n            'commander': 'ray-v3.5',\n            'status': 'online',\n            'data': result,\n            'raw_length': len(raw)\n        }\n    return {\n        'commander': 'ray-v3.5',\n        'status': 'parse_failed',\n        'raw': raw[:300],\n        'raw_length': len(raw)\n    }\n\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    import requests\n    print(\"=== ray-v3.5 JSON 提取測試 ===\")\n    resp = requests.post('http://localhost:11434/api/generate', json={\n        'model': 'ray-v3.5',\n        'prompt': 'TSLA 245 RSI65 VIX18. JSON: {action,confidence,reason}',\n        'stream': False,\n        'options': {'num_predict': 400, 'temperature': 0.3}\n    }, timeout=30)\n    raw = resp.json().get('response', '')\n    print(f\"Raw length: {len(raw)}\")\n    result = parse_ray_response(raw)\n    if result.get('data'):\n        d = result['data']\n        print(f\"\\n✅ Action: {d.get('action', d.get('a', '?'))}\")\n        print(f\"✅ Confidence: {d.get('confidence', d.get('c', '?'))}\")\n        print(f\"✅ Reason: {d.get('reason', d.get('r', '?'))[:60]}...\")\n    else:\n        print(f\"❌ Parse failed, raw[:200]: {raw[:200]}\")","path":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\ray_nl2code.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":241,"output":787,"cacheRead":86272,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":87300,"cost":{"input":0.0000723,"output":0.0009444,"cacheRead":0.00517632,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00619302}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778605952380,"responseId":"06529282a07ec469c80dea37355fbf89"}}
