{"type":"message","id":"5b74fd39","parentId":"837813da","timestamp":"2026-05-12T17:16:27.749Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Jo wants me to integrate all system scripts and scheduling with 7B and 4B local LLM. This means:\n\n1. All existing scripts need to be updated to use the new 4B/7B layer model\n2. The scheduler needs to coordinate everything\n3. Cron jobs need to be aligned with the 4B/7B split\n\nLet me check what scripts currently exist that need to be updated, and also check the current cron jobs and their status.\n\nLet me first check the current state of:\n1. Cron jobs (what's scheduled)\n2. All scripts that call Ollama models\n3. The llm_router.py integration\n\n\n4. I need to verify all the scripts that reference models - things like ray_brain.py, ray_integrated_brain.py, ray_web_learner.py, and ray_econ_learner.py are likely calling models directly and need to be updated to route through the unified router instead.\n","thinkingSignature":"9430d6e0ba93d9f080e20f3873942362415ff69be25633b70b04a92b8ddbdf80"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n好，全面整合。先盤點現有腳本與排程：\n\n[Assistant tool calls]: exec(command=\"Get-ChildItem \\\"C:\\\\Users\\\\USER\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\ray\\\\*.py\\\" | Where-Object { $_.Length -gt 5000 } | Select-Object Name, Length | Sort-Object Length -Descending | Select-Object -First 15; echo \\\"---\\\"; Get-ChildItem \\\"C:\\\\Users\\\\USER\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\Tina_Quant_System\\\\scripts\\\\*.py\\\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Select-Object Name, Length | Sort-Object Length -Descending | Select-Object -First 10\")</parameter>\n<parameter name=\"timeout\">10</parameter>\n</invoke>\n"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":381,"output":351,"cacheRead":91264,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91996,"cost":{"input":0.0001143,"output":0.0004212,"cacheRead":0.005475839999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.006011339999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timesta