{"type":"message","id":"88fa03a8","parentId":"828d8f58","timestamp":"2026-05-12T17:17:57.824Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Jo wants to do a comprehensive backtest:\n- 4B (ray-v3.5) and 7B (ray-deep-v1) working in sequence\n- TW stocks: 500 stocks\n- US stocks: 500 stocks\n- Historical trading backtest\n\nThis is a major task. Let me understand the scope:\n- TW 500 stocks x historical data x multiple strategies = massive computation\n- US 500 stocks same\n\nI need to:\n1. Build a proper backtest system that uses ray-v3.5 (4B) and ray-deep-v1 (7B) sequentially\n2. The 4B does fast screening/proposal, 7B does deep analysis\n\n\n3. Schedule this properly\n\nFor the backtest pipeline, I need to process each stock through the two-model system: ray-v3.5 generates initial signal candidates, then ray-deep-v1 validates and filters them based on Sharpe ratio and max drawdown requirements. The raw price data feeds into local technical indicators, then the 4B proposes entry/exist points for each stock, and the 7B filters down to the strongest signals before returning the final validated list.\n\nFor the operational schedule, this is a massive job that needs to run during quiet hours—either after midnight EST when US markets close or on weekends when there's no trading pressure. I'm thinking 500 stocks per region × 1-2 minutes per stock × 2 models = roughly 16-33 hours of continuous processing, so Sunday morning Taiwan time would be ideal to fit within the quiet period before Asian markets open.\n\nI should build a comprehensive script that handles the full pipeline: data fetching, feature calculation, dual-model backtesting, and results storage. Rather than running everything at once, I'll structure it to process in batches to avoid overwhelming the system.\n","thinkingSignature":"c630805cb4e378eac8f61601aab6da23845a0e8192196d8543ed1b47201a7064"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n好，目標明確：**4B+7B 依序對 TW 500檔 / US 500檔做歷史回測**。\n\n先建底層框架，再排時段。\n\n---\n\n**第一步：建 TW 500 檔回測引擎**\n[Assistant tool calls]: write\n<parameter name=\"content\"># -*- coding: utf-8 -*-\n\"\"\"\nray_backtest_master.py — 雙模型歷史回測系統\n==============================================\n4B (ray-v3.5) + 7B (ray-deep-v1)依序作戰\n\n流程：\n  Layer 0: 本地計算（不佔 LLM）- RSI / MA / ATR / 動量\n  Layer 1: ray-v3.5 (4B) — 快速策略提案（RSI2 均值回歸 / 趨勢追蹤）\n  Layer 2: ray-deep-v1 (7B) — 深度歸因（過濾 + 止損/持有天數確認）\n\nTarget:\n  TW: 500 檔（上市+上櫃）\n  US: 500 檔（SP500 + NASDAQ100）\n\"\"\"\n\nimport os, sys, json, time, sqlite3, warnings\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\nfrom typing import List, Dict, Optional, Tuple\nfrom concurrent.futures import ThreadPoolExecutor, as_completed\n\nwarnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\nsys.stdout.reconfigure(encoding='utf-8', errors='replace')\n\n# ── 路徑 ────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nAGENTS_DIR = r\"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\"\nDB_DIR = r\"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\"\nsys.path.insert(0, AGENTS_DIR)\n\n# ── 資料庫 ────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nBACKTEST_DB = os.path.join(AGENTS_DIR, \"ray_backtest.db\")\n\n# ── 模型 ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nMODEL_4B = \"ray-v3.5\"\nMODEL_7B = \"ray-deep-v1\"\nOLLAMA = \"http://localhost:11434/api/generate\"\n\n# ── 回測參數 ─────────────────────────────────────────────────\nINITIAL_CAPITAL = 1_000_000   # 100 萬\nMAX_POSITIONS = 10\nMAX_HOLD_DAYS = 20\nSTOP_LOSS_PCT = 0.05          # 5% 止損\nTRAILING_PCT = 0.10           # 10% 移動停損\n\n# ── 風控門檻 ─────────────────────────────────────────────────\nMIN_SHARPE = 1.5\nMAX_MDD = 0.15                # 15%\nMIN_TRADES = 20               # 至少 20 筆交易\n\n\n# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\n# Layer 0: 本地指標計算（純數學，零 LLM 成本）\n# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\ndef compute_indicators(df) -> Dict:\n    \"\"\"計算本地技術指標（不耗 LLM token）\"\"\"\n    close = df['close'].values\n    high = df['high'].values\n    low = df['low'].values\n    volume = df['volume'].values\n\n    # RSI(2) — Connors 核心\n    delta = np.diff(close)\n    gain = np.where(delta > 0, delta, 0)\n    loss = np.where(delta < 0, -delta, 0)\n    avg_gain = pd.Series(gain).rolling(2).mean().values\n    avg_loss = pd.Series(loss).rolling(2).mean().values\n    rs = avg_gain / (avg_loss + 1e-10)\n    rsi2 = 100 - (100 / (1 + rs))\n\n    # MA20 / MA60\n    ma20 = pd.Series(close).rolling(20).mean().values\n    ma60 = pd.Series(close).rolling(60).mean().values\n\n    # ATR(14)\n    hl = high - low\n    hc = np.abs(high - np.roll(close, 1))\n    lc = np.abs(low - np.roll(close, 1))\n    tr = np.maximum(hl, np.maximum(hc[1:], lc[1:]))\n    atr14 = pd.Series(tr).rolling(14).mean().values\n\n    # 動量 (1D / 5D / 20D)\n    mom1d = (close[-1] / close[-2] - 1) * 100 if len(close) >= 2 else 0\n    mom5d = (close[-1] / close[-6] - 1) * 100 if len(close) >= 6 else 0\n    mom20d = (close[-1] / close[-21] - 1) * 100 if len(close) >= 21 else 0\n\n    return {\n        'rsi2': float(rsi2[-1]) if not np.isnan(rsi2[-1]) else 50,\n        'rsi14': float(rs[-1] if len(rs) > 0 else 50),\n        'ma20': float(ma20[-1]) if not np.isnan(ma20[-1]) else close[-1],\n        'ma60': float(ma60[-1]) if not np.isnan(ma60[-1]) else close[-1],\n        'atr14': float(atr14[-1]) if not np.isnan(atr14[-1]) else 0,\n        'mom1d': float(mom1d),\n        'mom5d': float(mom5d),\n        'mom20d': float(mom20d),\n        'price': float(close[-1]),\n        'volume_avg': float(np.mean(volume[-20:])),\n        'vol_ratio': float(volume[-1] / np.mean(volume[-20:])) if np.mean(volume[-20:]) > 0 else 0,\n    }\n\n\n# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\n# Layer 1: 4B 快速策略提案\n# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\ndef call_4b_signal(symbol: str, ind: Dict, model: str = MODEL_4B) -> Dict:\n    \"\"\"ray-v3.5: 快速策略提案（< 5 秒）\"\"\"\n    import requests\n    prompt = f\"\"\"{symbol} price={ind['price']:.0f} RSI2={ind['rsi2']:.0f} MA20={ind['ma20']:.0f} MA60={ind['ma60']:.0f} ATR={ind['atr14']:.2f} momentum_20d={ind['mom20d']:.1f}%\nJSON: {{\"action\":\"BUY|WATCH|SELL|REJECT\",\"confidence\":0.0-1.0,\"strategy\":\"RSI2|MA_CROSS|MOMENTUM\",\"entry_reason\":\"...\"}}\nNo thinking. JSON only.\"\"\"\n    try:\n        resp = requests.post(OLLAMA, json={\n            \"model\": model,\n            \"prompt\": prompt,\n            \"stream\": False,\n            \"options\": {\"temperature\": 0.3, \"num_predict\": 150}\n        }, timeout=15)\n        raw = resp.json().get('response', '')\n        # Extract JSON\n        import re, json as _json\n        text = re.sub(r'<\\|think\\|>.*?<\\|/think\\|>', '', raw, flags=re.DOTALL)\n        text = re.sub(r'"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":372,"output":5663,"cacheRead":91456,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":97491,"cost":{"input":0.00011159999999999999,"output":0.0067956,"cacheRead":0.005487359999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.012394559999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778606198307,"responseId":"06529379a2ed8f49297c8092f5fc93e3"}}
